Die Entscheidung]],name=[[Attack On Highbridge: Denouement]],class_level=26,help_en=[[Join the Brass Blades in rescuing the Highbridge residents kidnapped by the Qiqirn bandits and slay the mastermind behind this dark design─Nayokk Roh.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ハイブリッジの死闘：市民奪還作戦]],},[196]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[197]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[198]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[199]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[200]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[201]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[202]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[203]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[204]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[205]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[206]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[207]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Chevalier Des Ombres]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dunkle Reiter]],name=[[Steel Reign]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Atop his mighty steed, clad in armor darker than the void, the elder primal Odin has returned to Eorzea to exact his brutal judgment upon the realm.]],name_ja=[[古の闘神「オーディン」]],},[208]={name_fr=[[Massacre D'insectes]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Käfer Außer Rand Und Band]],name=[[Lady Killer]],class_level=7,help_en=[[Ladybugs are more than welcome to dine on the aphids which infest the orchards of the Central Shroud; however, some have acquired a taste for the honeybees who pollinate the crops. See that this meal is their last.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[レディキラー]],},[209]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Géant Vert]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Essen Macht Durstig]],name=[[My Baby Green]],class_level=31,help_en=[[An overgrown tangle of vivified vines lovingly named Jaded Jody is drinking up all the water of Hopeseed Pond. If action is not taken quickly, the whole area will be dry by the next moon.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[水源の破壊者「ジェイデッド・ジョディ」]],},[212]={name_fr=[[Les Envahisseurs]],class_level_max=24,name_de=[[Neunundneunzig Efeuranken]],name=[[Ivy League]],class_level=19,help_en=[[Some species of ivy will continue growing until they have choked the life out of the entire forest. Assist both the Wood Wailers and the Gods' Quiver in their joint effort to clear the Twelveswood of this menace.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[ナインティナインアイビー]],},[213]={name_fr=[[L'offrande]],class_level_max=28,name_de=[[Von Den Sylphen Verweht]],name=[[Thunderstruck]],class_level=23,help_en=[[Sylphs tempered in the levin-light of the primal Ramuh have descended into Little Solace to abduct their untempered brethren. Protect the innocent by delivering lightning-swift justice to the perpetrators.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[シルフと共に去りぬ]],},[214]={name_fr=[[Le Festin Des Vautours]],class_level_max=16,name_de=[[Geierschmaus]],name=[[Carrion Baggage]],class_level=11,help_en=[[Scraps of food left scattered along forest thoroughfares by goblin travelers are attracting all sorts of carrion-craving cloudkin, who, when the fodder is gone, set their sights on poor Lalafellin pilgrims. Discourage further vultures from frequenting the region by slaying the ones already here.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[禿鷲の饗宴]],},[215]={name_fr=[[Pas De Pitié Pour Les Truands]],class_level_max=29,name_de=[[Wie Motten Zum Licht]],name=[[Conspiracy Theory]],class_level=24,help_en=[[High-ranking members of the Redbelly Wasps have gathered in an abandoned hovel to discuss their next attack on Gridania's trade routes. See that they do not leave alive.]],map={placename={name=[[South Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[飛んで火に入る似我蜂団]],},[216]={name_fr=[[Les Rejetons De La Lune Rouge]],class_level_max=33,name_de=[[Mondgestein]],name=[[Waiting For A Moon To Fall]],class_level=28,help_en=[[Remnants of Dalamud fallen from the celestial satellite have been reanimated by some sinister force, and now roam the region in the form of powerful golems. Destroy the soulkin before they wreak their havoc on the forest.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[月の反逆者]],},[217]={name_fr=[[L'appel De L'hydromel]],class_level_max=26,name_de=[[Die Süße Versuchung]],name=[[What Have You Done For Mead Lately]],class_level=21,help_en=[[A divine rite is being planned at the Sanctum of the Twelve and the clergy require copious amounts of freshly brewed mead to...uh, purify their spirits. Escort the porter and see that the mead arrives safely.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[甘い香りの運び人]],},[218]={name_fr=[[Défi: Laurence Pas Ravie]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Undank Des Faulen]],name=[[Lazy For You]],class_level=20,help_en=[[The things we love destroy us every time. So it was with Farmer Laurence, who was devoured by his grossly overgrown pet ochu which he named after himself. Slay the rampant creature, that the old farmer's soul might know peace.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[非情な収穫者「レジー・ローレンス」]],},[220]={name_fr=[[Défi: Menuis Le Terrible]],class_level_max=13,name_de=[[Aus Dir Mach Ich Suppe]],name=[[Menuis At Work]],class_level=8,help_en=[[The once-gentle aurochs living in the Cookpot have grown bold since the arrival of a bull known as Menuis. Slay the beast and show the other creatures who it is they should truly fear.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[巨躯の猛牛「メヌイス」]],},[221]={name_fr=[[Migration Nocturne]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Schlimmer Als Unkraut]],name=[[Overnight Migration]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Not only did the Calamity bring with it destruction, pain, and suffering, but it also brought with it mandragoras. Thousands and thousands of mandragoras. Mandragoras who, if not dealt with swiftly and firmly, will continue to multiply until the land is overrun with the creatures.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[サマーフォードの怪]],},[222]={name_fr=[[Ça Va Piquer]],class_level_max=18,name_de=[[Palastrevolte]],name=[[Go Wespe]],class_level=13,help_en=[[The Yellowjackets stationed in middle La Noscea have a royal problem. Wespes so large the smallfolk have dubbed them “kings” are terrorizing the countryside and need to be dethroned immediately.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ヴェスパとイエロージャケット]],},[223]={name_fr=[[Un Homme à Abattre]],class_level_max=19,name_de=[[Die Harte Schule]],name=[[A Mad, Mad, Mad Sergeant]],class_level=14,help_en=[[The storm soldiers stationed at the De Nevelle Checkpoint are short a few men, and require volunteers to aid them with their regular training exercises in which they attempt to fend off a mock imperial assault.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[デネベール関門防衛訓練]],},[225]={name_fr=[[Taupe Départ]],class_level_max=11,name_de=[[Mulle Auf Die Stulle]],name=[[Thwack-a-Mole]],class_level=6,help_en=[[The orchards of middle La Noscea are riddled with dangerous holes dug by Moraby moles. It is high time the pests were given a good thumping.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[果てなきモグラ叩き]],},[226]={name_fr=[[Pitoyables Recrues]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Übermut Tut Selten Gut]],name=[[Yellow-bellied Greenbacks]],class_level=5,help_en=[[The newest batch of Yellowjacket recruits is softer than a rotten rat corpse, and fights little better. Whip the raw lads into shape. And remember, mercy is the last thing they need.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[海軍式の通過儀礼]],},[227]={name_fr=[[La Violence Des Agneaux]],class_level_max=8,name_de=[[Unter Schafen]],name=[[On The Lamb]],class_level=3,help_en=[[A flock of sheep bitten by diseased bats has grown frenzied and is charging at full speed towards the Zephyr Gate. The infected creatures cannot be allowed to enter the city, so they must be driven off or put down.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[羊たちの騒乱]],},[229]={name_fr=[[Les Caisses D'oranges]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Es Rappelt In Der Kiste]],name=[[The Orange Boxes]],class_level=9,help_en=[[Crates of freshly picked oranges waiting to be delivered to Galadion Bay's pleasure boats are in danger of being infested by rats lured by the sweet smell of the fruit. Drive back the vermin until the chocobo caravan arrives.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[上には上がある]],},[231]={name_fr=[[Défi: Qui S'y Frotte S'y Pique]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Das Große Krabbenpulen]],name=[[Shearing Is Caring]],class_level=10,help_en=[[Shearing Sheridan has been shearing his share of luckless passersby since long before the Calamity. What the megalocrab needs now is a good shell-shocking.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[切断狂「シアリング・シェリダン」]],},[233]={name_fr=[[L'enfant Qui Criait Au Loup]],class_level_max=19,name_de=[[Schalk Und Schakale Im Nacken]],name=[[The Boy Who Cried Jackal]],class_level=14,help_en=[[A young porter thought it would be clever to fool his companions into believing that they were being stalked by a pack of jackals so while the others were off hunting the beasts, he could slip off and frolic with a local milkmaid. The only problem being, jackals truly were stalking him, and now he's in a pickle.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[追う者と追われる者]],},[235]={name_fr=[[La Famille Avant Tout]],class_level_max=17,name_de=[[Nicht Ohne Meine Eier]],name=[[Sister Crustacean]],class_level=12,help_en=[[A spawning megalocrab will do whatever it takes to see its brood safe, and that includes slicing in half Lalafellin fishers who draw too close to the wavekin's unhatched offspring. Slay a crab, save a lad.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[その水棲動物を見よ]],},[237]={name_fr=[[De Nouvelles Perspectives]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Gekenterte Existenzen]],name=[[Hello, Work]],class_level=7,help_en=[[During the Calamity, many bands of pirates lost their ships to either Garlean attackers or the flames of Bahamut. Most found new crews to join, but those who didn't simply turned to banditry on land. Use your blades to convince the lads it is high time they seek new employment.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[農場にかける橋]],},[238]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Vérité Est Ailleurs]],class_level_max=19,name_de=[[Blut Geleckt]],name=[[The Truth Is Out There]],class_level=14,help_en=[[Middle La Noscea is abuzz following sightings of the Chupacabra─a dog-like creature rumored to drink the blood of virgins. Is the beast real, or just a legend!?]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[血濡れの猛犬「チュパカブラ」]],},[239]={name_fr=[[Nettoyage De Printemps]],class_level_max=9,name_de=[[Frischer Fisch Frisst Fischers Fische]],name=[[Taking It To The Streams]],class_level=4,help_en=[[The Rogue River has become a breeding ground for giant carnivorous fish known as pugils. Help clear the shallows so the local fishers can cast their lines in relative peace.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[麗しのローグ川]],},[240]={name_fr=[[Agriculture Sauvage]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Salziger Regen]],name=[[Crying Over Spilled Salt]],class_level=7,help_en=[[Coastal winds blow floating aureliae from their native habitat over the Rhotano Sea to the shores of middle La Noscea, where they release their salty ballast onto the soil, rendering it unsuitable for farming. Slay the creatures before they become the salt of the earth.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[クラゲが飛んだ日]],},[245]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Prince]],class_level_max=18,name_de=[[Der Albtraumprinz]],name=[[One Prince]],class_level=13,help_en=[[While little is known about mandragoras, what is known tends to be quite disturbing. Such is the case with the mandragora prince, who is rumored to journey to the sites of slaughters so it might feed off the blood-soaked loam. It is probably best to not let it feed off the blood-soaked loam.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[不吉なる王子「マンドラプリンス」]],},[246]={name_fr=[[Dangereux Végétaux]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Eine Rose Ist Eine Rose]],name=[[Fight The Flower]],class_level=5,help_en=[[They say every rose has its thorn. When it comes to roselings, however, thorns are the least of your problems. The strangling vines, the poisonous pollen, the ability to rise up from the ground and chase you all the way into your nightmares─these make roselings a force to be reckoned with...and the day of reckoning is come.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[危ない野良仕事]],},[249]={name_fr=[[Problème De Nuisibles]],class_level_max=9,name_de=[[Krötenplage]],name=[[You Call That A Toad]],class_level=4,help_en=[[When the wheat farmers of lower La Noscea were losing large portions of their crops to locusts, they turned to Maelvaan's Gate who introduced Cieldalaes cane toads to the fields to devour the vilekin. Unfortunately, the cane toads, who have no natural predators on Vylbrand, have taken over the region, leaving the farms with no choice but to slay them all.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[蛙の子は蛙]],},[250]={name_fr=[[Virus Fulgurant]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Fledermäuse Mit Biss]],name=[[Caving In]],class_level=7,help_en=[[The cave bats living in Blind Iron Mines are believed to carry in their bite a sickness which can cause a man to froth at the mouth and lust after the blood of his kin. While this has not actually been proven, when it comes to bat bites, it is better to be safe than sorry.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[黒い翼]],},[251]={name_fr=[[Vol De Farine]],class_level_max=13,name_de=[[Rätselhafte Galagos]],name=[[Man Of The Flour]],class_level=8,help_en=[[Galagos from nearby Raincatcher Gully have found their way into the granaries which store the flour milled by the Grey Fleet. Why galagos would want flour when there are berries aplenty in the jungle is a mystery that might never be solved because the millers want those galagos dead.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[小麦粉戦争]],},[257]={name_fr=[[Défi: Une Bonne Digestion]],class_level_max=8,name_de=[[Zum Dahinschmelzen]],name=[[I Melt With You]],class_level=3,help_en=[[Some creatures are best left alone. Cuachac is a giant jellyfish which consumes its prey by stunning it with its poisonous tentacles, then dousing it in a corrosive liquid which slowly reduces the prey into an easy-to-digest pile of gelatinous ooze. Cuachac is best not left alone. Cuachac must be slain.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[浮かぶ胃袋「クアハック」]],},[260]={name_fr=[[Mise Au Placard]],class_level_max=16,name_de=[[Blinder Passagier]],name=[[Away In A Bilge Hold]],class_level=11,help_en=[[Men of a Yellowjacket patrol have cornered a stowaway they believe might be the notorious Ahctstymm Shadowlurker, but the ne'er-do-well has elected to put up a fight. The Yellowjackets could use any aid nearby adventurers might offer.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[迷惑千万「密航のアクトシュティム」]],},[261]={name_fr=[[Défi: Au Nom De L'amour]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Liebe Reimt Sich Auf Hiebe]],name=[[In The Name Of Love]],class_level=10,help_en=[[Unemployed pirates Anselm Larkscall and Fiebras the Dull are fighting again, more than likely over the same woman they were with last night. A little cold steel should help the two cool their heads.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[俺たちゃ海賊]],},[262]={name_fr=[[Eau Non Potable]],class_level_max=17,name_de=[[Wir Müssen Draußen Bleiben]],name=[[Don't Drink The Water]],class_level=12,help_en=[[Despite being surrounded on all sides by the sea, fresh water remains difficult to come by on Vylbrand, which is why the few springs that do exist must be protected at all costs from blighted dodos and jackals who come to the water to drink...and defecate.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[水場の争い]],},[264]={name_fr=[[L'éveil Des Bêtes]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Lauter Klabauter]],name=[[Enter Beastman]],class_level=9,help_en=[[The kobolds of O'Ghomoro have once again descended into Cedarwood, blatantly disregarding the treaty formed between the beast tribe and Limsa Lominsa which strictly forbids the kobolds from extending their claims beyond the northern reaches of outer La Noscea. Drive the creatures back to the mountains whence they came.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[シダーウッドの戦い]],},[265]={name_fr=[[Bonne Pioche]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Dafür Gibt's Haue]],name=[[One Pickman Enters]],class_level=9,help_en=[[Enraged by their defeat in Cedarwood, the kobolds have summoned one of their champions, 426th Order Pickman Bu Ga, to avenge the loss. Make swift work of the creature so he knows not to return.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[精強なる山師「ピックマン426 ブ・ガ」]],},[267]={name_fr=[[Partage De La Soif]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Mein Wein Bleibt Mein Wein]],name=[[Finding Wine]],class_level=32,help_en=[[A band of buccaneers is bound for the borders of the bustling borough of Wineport in search of beverages to sate their bacchanalian cravings. Steer the scoundrels from the settlement while seeing they stay sober.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ワインよこせ！]],},[268]={name_fr=[[Plan De Poivrots]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Seeräubersommelier In Spe]],name=[[The Thirst]],class_level=32,help_en=[[A band of parched buccaneers are looking to quench their thirsts the pirate way─a good old-fashioned raid─and have gathered in a copse near Wineport to hammer out their plan of attack. Join the Maelstrom in stopping the attack before it can happen.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ワイン飲みてぇ！]],},[271]={name_fr=[[Peur Du Vide]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Frischfleischlieferung]],name=[[Thrill Of The Hunt]],class_level=33,help_en=[[A moment in the bushes to drain the morning dew is all it took for a poor Lominsan merchant to be left behind by his caravan. Now, to make matters worse, he is being tracked by a pack of raptors who see the hapless hawker as naught more than a light snack. Slay the scalekin and protect the merchant.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[新鮮な生肉]],},[272]={name_fr=[[Appel Aux Pélicans]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Wo Gesammelt Wird, Da Fliegen Federn]],name=[[The Pelican Briefing]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Jijiroon of Jijiroon's Trading Post is looking to replenish his stock of pelican eggs─a favorite amongst Qiqirn─and has traveled all the way to eastern La Noscea to do so. Assist the enterprising beastman by slaying pelicans, collecting their eggs, and delivering them before they hatch!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[エッグモンスター]],},[274]={name_fr=[[Microcosme]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Mantis Mantis Timpe Te]],name=[[Them]],class_level=33,help_en=[[A cluster of red mantis eggs has hatched and now the jungle is crawling with tiny red monsters. If not put down immediately, the jungle will soon be crawling with giant red monsters!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ミクロの決死隊]],},[278]={name_fr=[[Maudites Moustaches]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Rattige Hausbesetzer]],name=[[Careless Whiskers]],class_level=30,help_en=[[A flea-ridden pack of Qiqirn is attempting to transform the sorely undermanned Gullperch Tower into a rat nest. Drive the beastmen off before they get a tailhold.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[白い巨塔]],},[279]={name_fr=[[Colibris Voleurs]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Kalkreiche Kost]],name=[[No Lip]],class_level=33,help_en=[[The Bloodshore colibri are devouring the area's rainbowlip oysters, leaving none for the poor young women who maintain their livelihood by selling the shells to Ul'dahn goldsmiths. Slay the gluttonous birds and retrieve the shells from the corpses' bellies.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[コリブリたちの食卓]],},[280]={name_fr=[[Défi: Voler Aux Riches]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Was Auf Die Finger]],name=[[Jewels Of The Isle]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Notorious sneak thief Kokoroon Quickfingers has been sighted swiping jewelry from the lockboxes of wealthy Costa del Sol retirees. Find the bandit and give him a good thumping.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[彷徨の業師「弾指のココルン」]],},[282]={name_fr=[[La Fin Des Crabes]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Schnippische Schnippler]],name=[[Crab And Go]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Giant crabs known as snippers have invaded the once-pristine beaches of Bloodshore, making it difficult for Costa del Sol retirees to take their morning walks without having their raiments sliced to ribbons. The problem requires immediate attention, and adventurers are sought to cull the sidestepping sea creatures.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[海辺のスニッパー]],},[286]={name_fr=[[Suivez La Lumière]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Angriff Der Geisterpiraten]],name=[[Follow The Light]],class_level=33,help_en=[[The mischievous spirits of fallen pirates are luring drowsy Costa del Sol retirees from their bedchambers into the churning sea. Save the poor septuagenarians so that they may continue to spend their hard-earned wealth at the Flying Shark. Now open for brunch!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[死者の代弁者]],},[287]={name_fr=[[La Saison Des Amours]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Weibchenlos, Ledig, Jung]],name=[[Just A Matter Of Rut]],class_level=31,help_en=[[The buffaloes of Bloodshore are in rut, and a shortage of females this season means that the males who have yet to find mates are especially violent. Deal with the roused beasts before they harm themselves or others.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[愛はさだめ、さだめは死]],},[289]={name_fr=[[Livraison De Missive]],class_level_max=21,name_de=[[Für Nachschub Ist Gesorgt]],name=[[Absolutely, Positively]],class_level=16,help_en=[[An important missive from the Admiral must be delivered to South Tidegate. See to it the storm courier tasked with carrying the message reaches her destination unharmed.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[補給線を支えろ]],},[290]={name_fr=[[Défi: Volatile Carnivore]],class_level_max=17,name_de=[[Der Kleine Nimmersatt]],name=[[Tender Buttons]],class_level=12,help_en=[[Gluttonous Gertrude was just another plump dodo on the farm...until she bit the arse off one of the stable boys at Swiftperch and escaped into Quarterstone. Seek out the ravenous bird and slay her before another rump goes missing.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[暴食の怪鳥「グルタナスガーティ」]],},[291]={name_fr=[[Sauvagerie Animale]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Zwischen Ähren Liegt Ehre]],name=[[The Killing Fields]],class_level=10,help_en=[[The wheat fields abandoned after the Calamity have turned into a breeding ground for wild animals who prey on Swiftperch's crops and stock. Drive the creatures from the overgrowth and slay as many as possible.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[小麦畑でつかまえて]],},[295]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Crabe De Légende]],class_level_max=18,name_de=[[Sechs Richtige ... Arme]],name=[[(I Just) Died In Six Arms Tonight]],class_level=13,help_en=[[It is believed most crabs only live for two to three years─fewer if nearby Lominsans are hungry. There is one crab, however, that is rumored to have survived since the Fifth Astral Era, surviving on the blood of man (though no one can truly back that claim). All things must die, and Old Six-arms's time has come.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[古強者「オールドシックスアームズ」]],},[297]={name_fr=[[La Fin De La Contrebande]],class_level_max=23,name_de=[[Steuerprüfung]],name=[[Iron Contra Affair]],class_level=18,help_en=[[Goblins from Iron Lake, now encamped in Skull Valley, are peddling items strictly prohibited by thalassocratic decree. Yellowjackets stationed in the area are seeking to confiscate the contraband and are entreating adventurers for aid.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[税関公社の強制捜査]],},[298]={name_fr=[[De Redoutables Aquatiques]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Plündernde Schlangen]],name=[[Don't Call Him A Fishback]],class_level=17,help_en=[[The Serpent Reavers─mindless servants of the Sahagin─are raiding the farmsteads of western La Noscea, killing the men, savaging the women, and selling the children into servitude. Aid the Maelstrom in putting these foul turncloaks down.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[敵は海賊・海蛇の舌]],},[303]={name_fr=[[Lettres Du Front]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Grüße Aus Der Heimat]],name=[[Letters From Tidegate]],class_level=17,help_en=[[A letter carrier tasked with delivering messages from soldiers on the front lines back to their loved ones in Limsa Lominsa is being harassed by bandits who seek to claim the personal effects enclosed in the packages. Slay the perpetrators and defend the young man.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[故郷からの手紙]],},[304]={name_fr=[[Destruction De Nids]],class_level_max=17,name_de=[[Turtel-Dodos]],name=[[The Last Straw]],class_level=12,help_en=[[What nature did not reclaim of Quarterstone after the Calamity, the dodos did, but now it is time to take the land back. Destroy nests and drive the cloudkin from the fields, so that the settlers might piece back together their lives.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ドードーの巣破壊命令]],},[306]={name_fr=[[Défi: Soupe De Barometz]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Ausgewogene Ernährung]],name=[[Barometz Soup]],class_level=10,help_en=[[Already known for its size in the Sixth Astral Era, the overgrown landtrap Barometz has grown even larger since the Calamity, feeding on weakened dodos and aldgoats until reaching its current size of almost two score hands. Slice it down to size, or you might be its next victim!]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[死活の罠「バロメッツ」]],},[308]={name_fr=[[Barrage De Gobelins]],class_level_max=20,name_de=[[Geplatzte Verhandlungen]],name=[[Goblin Chain]],class_level=15,help_en=[[A band of goblins turned away from Aleport is taking out its frustrations on the hamlet by blockading its entrance. Put the creatures down so that business may carry on as usual.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[交渉決裂]],},[309]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'adieu Au Mercenaire]],class_level_max=23,name_de=[[Der Typ Rafft's Nicht]],name=[[Tryp Fantastic]],class_level=18,help_en=[[The goblins encamped in Skull Valley have hired a named mercenary to help them raid the nearby farmsteads. Hunt down Tryptix Stumblemox and slay him.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[愚鈍な用心棒「間抜のトリップティックス」]],},[310]={name_fr=[[Expulsion D'aurochs]],class_level_max=20,name_de=[[Straßenblockade]],name=[[Between Aurochs]],class_level=15,help_en=[[Several aurochs have begun grazing alongside the De Nevelle Westroad, frightening merchants and preventing the transport of goods to and from the area. Use any means necessary to urge the beasts from the thoroughfare.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[決闘デネベール街道]],},[312]={name_fr=[[Sac Mortel]],class_level_max=21,name_de=[[Erst Wimmeln, Dann Wimmern]],name=[[In The Sac]],class_level=16,help_en=[[A killer mantis egg sac has burst open, releasing countless of the deadly vilekin into western La Noscea. It is best they are slain now while young before given the opportunity to live up to their name.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[昆虫軍団現わる]],},[314]={name_fr=[[Défi: Simurgh Le Redoutable]],class_level_max=28,name_de=[[Schrecken Der Coeurl]],name=[[Simurgh Is The Word]],class_level=23,help_en=[[Simurgh, a colossal cloudkin who is thought to nest high upon O'Ghomoro, has descended into upper La Noscea to feed─his prey of choice? Lalafells. Slay the creature before he finds his next tender, juicy victim.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[豹喰いの妖鳥「シームルグ」]],},[317]={name_fr=[[Escorte Pour Le Guet]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Schutz Und Hilfe]],name=[[Surprise]],class_level=34,help_en=[[A lightly armed Maelstrom transportation unit en route to Camp Overlook has been ambushed by a band of savage kobolds. Fend off the assailants and protect the supply troops to ensure that the unit can complete its delivery.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[輸送部隊防衛命令]],},[320]={name_fr=[[Mamool Repart Chez Maman]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Heute Freund, Morgen Feind]],name=[[The Road More Traveled]],class_level=30,help_en=[[A party of Mamool Ja mercenaries hired by the local kobolds is attacking travelers using the main thoroughfares through upper La Noscea. Engage the mercenaries and make them regret ever taking this contract.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[昨日の友は今日の敵]],},[321]={name_fr=[[Frapper Dans L'œuf]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Schlammschlacht]],name=[[Nine-ilm Snails]],class_level=31,help_en=[[Not a day passes without the physickers of the Warmwine Sanitorium having to clean their bathing pools of uragnite hatchlings, and they have had enough. They seek volunteers to hunt down and slay the root of the problem─the adult creatures laying the eggs in the springs.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[湯煙温泉殺貝事件]],},[322]={name_fr=[[Défi: Attention, ça Mord]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Oannes Aus Dem Grünenden Weiher]],name=[[Truth In Faerie Tales]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Legend says deep beneath the waters of Bronze Lake dwells a terrible creature with jaws so powerful they can tear a man in two with a single bite. Common sense would suggest that Oannes is merely a tale to frighten babes, but the local smallfolk would have us believe otherwise.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[石緑湖の主「オアンネス」]],},[323]={name_fr=[[Défi: Crabe Qui Ne Pond Pas...]],class_level_max=26,name_de=[[Wehrhafte Delikatesse]],name=[[Giant Enemy Crab]],class_level=21,help_en=[[A crab released into Bronze Lake by Qiqirn so that the beastmen might harvest its sweet eggs has grown into an uncontrollable nuisance. Not only does it not produce any eggs of its own (on the account of being a male), it also ravages the nests of the local waterfowl, devouring their eggs. Karkinos must be slain.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[脅威の元食材「カルキノス」]],},[329]={name_fr=[[Défi: Prudence Avec L'eau Chaude...]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Kind Der Heißen Quellen]],name=[[Shell Shocked]],class_level=31,help_en=[[Heated by the molten rock coursing deep below O'Ghomoro, the waters of Bronze Lake are warm year-round. This unique environment has allowed creatures, which normally only grow to a few ilms, to balloon into terrifying monstrosities. The wavekin Zoredonite is one such abomination.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[温泉の申し子「ゾレドナイト」]],},[331]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Baigneur Gênant]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Tänzer Müssen Draußen Bleiben]],name=[[Peeping Ja]],class_level=33,help_en=[[After repeatedly harassing a party of Miqo'te bathers, a Mamool Ja mercenary who goes by the name of Scarface Bugaal Ja was banned for life from the hot springs at Camp Bronze Lake. The degenerate, however, is back once again, and must needs be dealt with.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[悲運の傭兵「美男のブガージャ」]],},[332]={name_fr=[[Trop D'œufs, Bonjour Les Dégâts]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Läufer überm Bronzesee]],name=[[Hop, Skip, And A Jump]],class_level=33,help_en=[[A plague of waterskipper yarzons has converged upon the shores of Bronze Lake, looking to lay eggs. Waterskipper numbers are already at an all-time high, and if any more were allowed to hatch, the area would be overrun with the ravenous pests. Slay the yarzons before they can mate.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[湖面を駆けろ！]],},[333]={name_fr=[[Défi: Lien Brisé]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Da Bist Du Platt]],name=[[Under The Bridge]],class_level=10,help_en=[[More and more merchants are refusing to make the trip to the Gods' Grip due to rumors of a giant wolf-like creature called Padfoot who is said to hide below Oschon's Embrace, attacking any who attempt to cross the bridge. Hunt the beast down and restore peace to the area.]],map={placename={name=[[Lower La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[豪然たる魔犬「パッドフット」]],},[334]={name_fr=[[Complainte D'une Fille De Choix]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Frühlingsnachtstraum]],name=[[Consigned, Sealed, And Undelivered]],class_level=33,help_en=[[An important client of Master Gegeruju's─one Aismurl Goldmember─is visiting Costa del Sol to complete a sizable business transaction. To ensure that things go smoothly, the master has prepared a special incentive for his guest...and she requires proper escort to Hidden Falls.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[夏への扉]],},[335]={name_fr=[[Défi: Cancer, Le Casque De Mort]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Krabbe XXL]],name=[[It's Not Lupus]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Claws so powerful they can split a rock in two. A shell so hard, not even the hammer of a mighty hecatoncheir can crack it. Cancer, a crab rumored to have been spawned in the heavens, has appeared in eastern La Noscea. Slay him and become the stuff of legends!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[死顔の簒奪者「キャンサー」]],},[336]={name_fr=[[Le Gang Des Légumes]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.3]],},name_de=[[Die Botanische Revolution]],name=[[The Mandragoras]],class_level=45,help_en=[[Sensing weakness in the realm following the Calamity, five rogue vegetables (well, technically four and a fruit) have risen up to rid the land of all meat─including YOU. Cool off the Mandragoras before their verdant insurgence gains steam.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[野菜革命「マンドラーズ」]],},[342]={name_fr=[[Épineux Végétaux]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Chaos In Grün]],name=[[Needles To Slay]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Needles shed by cactuars are the number four cause of foot irritation in all western Thanalan. By slaying a few cactuars, we can see that number drop to sixth, or even seventh!]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[緊急停止]],},[343]={name_fr=[[Investir Dans La Pierre]],class_level_max=11,name_de=[[Knabberspaß]],name=[[Things That Make You Go Home]],class_level=6,help_en=[[Land purchased by a wealthy real estate mogul for development into luxury estates has become overrun with yarzons. Slay the vilekin before someone sees them and property values drop.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[強制立ち退き]],},[344]={name_fr=[[V Pour Vandalisme]],class_level_max=13,name_de=[[V Wie Vandalen]],name=[[Deface The Facts]],class_level=8,help_en=[[Now banished from Ul'dah for various acts of vandalism and basic thuggery, a gang of unruly, yet simply adorable, goblin muggers has made its way to Hammerlea where the beastmen have found a new favorite pastime─the destruction of random items lying about the Hammers. It is time they were shown some tough love.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[階級的怒りの鉄槌]],},[345]={name_fr=[[Bruyants Volatiles]],class_level_max=13,name_de=[[Hammerharte Hammerschnäbel]],name=[[Please Hammers, Don't Hurt Them]],class_level=8,help_en=[[Hammer beaks have drawn too close to the Silver Bazaar for comfort, causing many a sleepless night for the hamlet's residents. Become the anvil which stops the cloudkin's advance.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[大地のハンマー]],},[346]={name_fr=[[Le Nerf De La Terre]],class_level_max=13,name_de=[[Der Kern Der Sache]],name=[[The Cores]],class_level=8,help_en=[[The workers of Hammerlea require earth sprite cores to help harden the land before they can drive their massive piles.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ミッション・アース]],},[347]={name_fr=[[Défi: Maudit Crapaud Maudit]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Verdammt Und Verdorben]],name=[[Doomed]],class_level=9,help_en=[[Before the Calamity, the Brass Blades were flooded with reports of a giant toad-like creature roaming the desert, lapping up poor Lalafellin travelers with its long, sticky tongue. Now, ten summers later, rumors of a “doomed gigantoad” are surfacing once again.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[謎の巨大生物「ドゥーム・ギガントード」]],},[348]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Hors-la-loi]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Kaktor Jack]],name=[[The Villain]],class_level=9,help_en=[[No one knows why Cactuar Jack feels the need to rain his hundred needles down upon all who happen by, because few have lived long enough to ask him...not that he would answer if he were asked, or that anyone would be able to understand him if he were to answer.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[砂漠の覇王「カクター・ジャック」]],},[349]={name_fr=[[La Peste Soit Des Peistes]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Wegelagerer]],name=[[Copied Peistes]],class_level=10,help_en=[[The shorthanded Brass Blades desperately seek aid in ridding the area of deadly peistes, who, without any predators save man, continue to multiply at an alarming rate.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[荒野の用心棒]],},[350]={name_fr=[[Attention, Hourets Méchants]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Gemischte Gefühle]],name=[[Dog Eat Dog]],class_level=10,help_en=[[Feral packs of diseased dogs roam the desert attacking anyone carrying anything resembling food...or anyone resembling food, for that matter. Put the beasts down before a poor Lalafell becomes lunch.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[野良犬たちの挽歌]],},[352]={name_fr=[[Sauvetage De Pêcheurs]],class_level_max=18,name_de=[[Orobon Overkill]],name=[[Bigger Fish To Fry]],class_level=13,help_en=[[Unable or unwilling to tackle larger prey, orobon tend to feed on young fish. The lack of young fish leads to an eventual lack of old fish, putting those fishers of Crescent Cove who rely on the sea's bounty to make their living in quite a predicament. Help solve their trouble by dealing with the root of the problem.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[罪のない残虐]],},[353]={name_fr=[[Défi: Douceur Locale]],class_level_max=18,name_de=[[Bernie Gegen Den Rest Der Welt]],name=[[Bubble Trouble]],class_level=13,help_en=[[Several crab-loving fishers have journeyed to the Footfalls in search of a giant delicacy-to-be known to the locals as Bubbly Bernie. Unfortunately, without some help, it looks like the fishers are going to be the ones to get served.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[飽食の大蟹「バブリーバーニー」]],},[354]={name_fr=[[Attention, Sol Glissant]],class_level_max=27,name_de=[[Krankentransport]],name=[[Tripped Up By The Fruit Of Another]],class_level=22,help_en=[[A merchant en route to Vesper Bay was attacked by a pack of jackals after slipping and falling on a sun lemon rind left discarded by a traveling lemoncake monger. He requests an escort to the port town as he does not believe he can make it alone.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[負傷者を護送せよ]],},[355]={name_fr=[[Les Décombres Du Juggernaut]],class_level_max=28,name_de=[[Die Kämpfe Dauern Fort]],name=[[Juggernaut Down]],class_level=23,help_en=[[A unit of Garlean soldiers is sifting through the wreckage of a fallen imperial juggernaut, presumably searching for any salvageable pieces of magitek equipment. Engage the unit and see its members are unable to report their findings to Castrum Marinum.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[戦いは、なおも続いた]],},[356]={name_fr=[[Une Question De Minerai]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Kobalos-Wanderung]],name=[[A Matter Of Rust]],class_level=5,help_en=[[After devouring all the ore remaining in a nearby abandoned mine, a sizable pack of coblyns has set out into the desert in search of new feeding grounds. Amajina & Sons will suffer the pilfering of their yet-to-be-claimed resources no more, and seek the immediate eradication of the pests.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[コブラン族の大移動]],},[357]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Gênant Géant]],class_level_max=26,name_de=[[Die Riesen Sind Los]],name=[[There Might Be Giants]],class_level=21,help_en=[[A giant in Thanalan! It is not yet known whence he came, but it is known whither he must needs go─straight to the seventh hell!]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[黄金兜の大巨人「悲嘆のブリアレオス」]],},[361]={name_fr=[[Coup Sur Coup]],class_level_max=15,name_de=[[Schnabelweise Vögel]],name=[[Pound For Pound]],class_level=10,help_en=[[The incessant hammering of hammer beaks' hammer-like beaks is causing local settlers a great deal of lost sleep. Help the poor smallfolk strike at their problem while the iron is hot.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ハンマーチャンス]],},[366]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Monstre Aux Grandes Pattes]],class_level_max=27,name_de=[[Opa Lässt Das Meucheln Nicht]],name=[[He's Got Legs]],class_level=22,help_en=[[Unofficial studies conducted by unauthorized persons claim that more Ul'dahn children are orphaned by bloody attacks on their parents by a terrible creature called Daddy Longlegs than by any other means. In the time you take to question this claim, another child may be orphaned. Are you willing to take that risk!?]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[足長おやじ「ダディーロングレッグ」]],},[367]={name_fr=[[Retour à La Mort]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Geisterjäger]],name=[[Staying Dead]],class_level=20,help_en=[[The restless spirits of fishers lost at sea have wandered back, unable to break their ties with the corporeal world. Purify these poor souls so that they may continue their journey into Thal's realm.]],map={placename={name=[[Western Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ゴーストバスター]],},[370]={name_fr=[[Défi: Quelque Chose à Prouver]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Kräftemessen]],name=[[Something To Prove]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Ever since being denied entry into the Pugilists', Gladiators', Lancers', Marauders', and Archers' Guilds, Grishild the Ungood has taken to challenging anyone and everyone to duels, hoping to prove her detractors wrong. Or perhaps she's simply a masochist.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[粗野な勝負師「無頼のグリスヒルド」]],},[373]={name_fr=[[Comme Un Triton Hors De L'eau]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Füttern Verboten]],name=[[Like An Eft Out Of Water]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Drawn by the sumptuous scent of roasting meat and hot mulled wine, efts have crawled out from the muddy flats of their normal habitat to dine at nearby cookfires. Slay a few so that the kindly father may roast them up for his starveling sons.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[夕飯を渡すな！]],},[374]={name_fr=[[Ivres Comme Des Rats]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Revolution Der Ratten]],name=[[Wrecked Rats]],class_level=7,help_en=[[Cockeyed Qiqirn denied entry to the Coffer & Coffin have not taken the news well and are causing trouble for the heavy who was hired to keep characters like these from causing trouble. Lend the poor lad a hand in helping the beastmen sober up.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[底無の酒豪「飲んべえググルン」]],},[375]={name_fr=[[Des Rats Bien Téméraires]],class_level_max=11,name_de=[[Die Würfel Sind Gefallen]],name=[[Survivor Rats]],class_level=6,help_en=[[A band of Qiqirn bandits has left its camp in search of fresh prey, and the Brass Blades are bent on seeing the beastmen's efforts end in failure. All aid provided by adventurers will be noted and duly rewarded.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[コッファー与えず、コフィンに送れ]],},[376]={name_fr=[[Défi: Fêlure]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Windelweich Gekocht]],name=[[Cracked]],class_level=9,help_en=[[As his colorful moniker suggests, notorious Qiqirn bandit Babaroon Halfshell prefers his prey firm on the outside and runny on the inside─something to keep in mind when he has you in an iron cookpot, boiling over an open flame. Now get cracking before he grows hungry.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[半熟英雄「半熟のババルン」]],},[377]={name_fr=[[Animé Par La Vengeance]],class_level_max=19,name_de=[[Ein Angler Am Haken]],name=[[Orobon Part Two: The Spawning]],class_level=14,help_en=[[A poor boy whose father was eaten by an orobon (yes, an orobon) has sworn bloody revenge against the terrible wavekin who rendered him a starveling orphan. While it won't bring his father back, the indiscriminate slaying of random orobon may just help restore the sparkle in the young boy's eyes.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[殺人魚スポーニングキラー]],},[378]={name_fr=[[Salade De Cactuars]],class_level_max=10,name_de=[[Mein Kleiner Grüner Kaktor]],name=[[Let Them Eat Cactus]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Appalled that the displaced souls living in the shantytowns beneath the towering city walls of Ul'dah are driven to eat rat tails and coblyn legs just to survive, the sultana has ordered her subjects to procure edible cactus leaves and distribute them to the starving masses.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[サボテンサラダ]],},[379]={name_fr=[[Pour La Reine]],class_level_max=14,name_de=[[Ameisen Auf Wohnungssuche]],name=[[For The Queen]],class_level=9,help_en=[[Giant antling sentries are on the march, most likely in search of Lalafellin children to snatch up and take back to their queen. Slay the vilekin before they catch the scent of a plump, innocent morsel.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[アリだー！]],},[381]={name_fr=[[Le Manoir Aux Voleurs]],class_level_max=16,name_de=[[Identitätsdiebe]],name=[[A Few Arrows Short Of A Quiver]],class_level=11,help_en=[[The summer home of Eolande Quiveron─former Syndicate member, before tragically losing her life in the Calamity─has been occupied by thieving bandits, one even claiming, in fact, to be the noble lady's heir. Rumor has it the bandits use the run-down manor to hide their booty, and a merchant is seeking aid in recovering his stolen goods.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[キヴロン家の住人]],},[383]={name_fr=[[Massacre De Volatiles]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Freie Fahrt Für Freie Bürger]],name=[[Big Time]],class_level=7,help_en=[[Fear of being pummeled by sledgehammer beaks is preventing miners from delivering their ore to assayers in Ul'dah. The Brass Blades seek help in clearing the Royal Allagan Starway of any and all threats.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[街道をゆく]],},[385]={name_fr=[[Défi: Cruelle Créature]],class_level_max=19,name_de=[[Sadistisches Vergnügen]],name=[[Cold-blooded]],class_level=14,help_en=[[A terrible monster, known as Vodyanoi, living in the pools beneath the Unholy Heir has been seen dragging his victims into the water, where he lies upon them until they asphyxiate. One would think that the wavekin then eats his prey, but such is not the case, as the corpses are left to drift in the pools until they are consumed by jackals and carrion crows. Could it be that Vodyanoi kills merely for pleasure!?]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[不浄なる大蝦蟇「ヴォジャノーイ」]],},[389]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Accueil Brûlant]],class_level_max=12,name_de=[[Einen Kühlen Kopf Bewahren]],name=[[A Warm Welcome]],class_level=7,help_en=[[Descended from Coerthas in search of warm stones, a spriggan known in the north as Spitfire is terrorizing the local smallfolk and hoarding precious ores and gems intended for sale to the Goldsmiths' Guild. Give the crafty creature a good cuffing and send him on his way back home.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[怒れる宝主「スピットファイア」]],},[393]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sortie Du Nid]],class_level_max=17,name_de=[[Sein Letztes Kommando]],name=[[Leaving The Nest]],class_level=12,help_en=[[The nest commander─a giant antling from Hellsbrood Holes─is out hunting again. Volunteers are wanted to see the violent vilekin slain.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[砂城の猛将「ネストコマンダー」]],},[394]={name_fr=[[Des Chèvres Voraces]],class_level_max=24,name_de=[[Ganz Schön Bockig]],name=[[Men Who See Goats]],class_level=19,help_en=[[Packs of wild myotragus have left their mountain homes to forage in the lowlands. The beastkin are known to eat anything and everything, and if not stopped and driven back to the crags, they will more than likely consume what precious little foliage remains in Thanalan.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[野獣死すべし]],},[395]={name_fr=[[De Mortels Piquants]],class_level_max=20,name_de=[[Wer Anderen Eine Grube Gräbt]],name=[[License To Quill]],class_level=15,help_en=[[Tuco-tuco quills are prized for their durability, and sought by weavers across the realm to use as sewing and knitting needles. The spines of steelquill tuco-tucos, however, are a different story. When shed along the Royal Sunway, they can cause grievous injuries to chocobos and other beasts of burden who use the roads. Slay steelquill tuco-tucos, and keep the thoroughfares clear.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[その硬さ、鋼の如し]],},[397]={name_fr=[[En Route Vers L'ouest]],class_level_max=23,name_de=[[Vormarsch Der Amalj'aa]],name=[[Westward Bound]],class_level=18,help_en=[[An Amalj'aa unit has been sighted moving west, most likely to establish a new encampment closer to Ul'dah. The safety of the city-state is at stake. Crush the beastmen and send them running back to Zanr'ak.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[アマルジャ軍迎撃作戦]],},[398]={name_fr=[[Défi: Destruction De Camp]],class_level_max=23,name_de=[[Ein Paar Aufs Maul]],name=[[Bad Camp]],class_level=18,help_en=[[The Amalj'aa stationed in their eastern Thanalan encampment have begun preparing for a large-scale foray into Ul'dahn territory. Foil their plans by destroying supply crates and slaying the encampment leader, Glassjaw Nazagg Gah.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[侵攻作戦を阻止せよ]],},[400]={name_fr=[[Quel Bazar]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Verteidigung Des Goldbasars]],name=[[Bazaar Blood Triangle]],class_level=17,help_en=[[A unit of Amalj'aa raiders has forced its way into the Golden Bazaar in search of slaves and supplies. Aid the Brass Blades stationed in the hamlet in fending off the attackers.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ゴールドバザー防衛戦]],},[401]={name_fr=[[Défi: Deux Yalms Sous Terre]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Rendezvous Mit Dem Tod]],name=[[Grim Undertakings]],class_level=17,help_en=[[A malevolent spirit, freed from his subterranean prison when the Calamity unearthed the Invisible City, is indiscriminately attacking those who journey into the ruins in search of fortune and knowledge. Seek out the Undertaker and release his soul from the fetters of the corporeal realm.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[煉獄の墓掘人「アンダーテイカー」]],},[402]={name_fr=[[Esprits Malfaisants]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Räuber Und Gendarm]],name=[[Simple Minds]],class_level=17,help_en=[[A gang of mischievous imps fancying themselves footpads has taken to assaulting travelers passing through eastern Thanalan. Chase off the voidsent and see the roads safe once more.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[盗賊もどきの成敗]],},[406]={name_fr=[[Volonté Divine]],class_level_max=32,name_de=[[Den Spieß Umdrehen]],name=[[Manifest Destiny]],class_level=27,help_en=[[Amalj'aa lancers approach from the east! Engage the beastmen before they can reach Highbridge.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[東部戦線異状なし]],},[407]={name_fr=[[Défi: Comme Un œuf]],class_level_max=34,name_de=[[Zum Haare Raufen]],name=[[Spare The Hair]],class_level=29,help_en=[[An old wives' tale states that if the monster Gossamer comes to you in your sleep, you will awake as bald as a melon. Middle-aged men across the realm, unite─for the bane must be quelled!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[毛髪の簒奪者「ゴッサマー」]],},[409]={name_fr=[[Rose Des Sables]],class_level_max=31,name_de=[[Unerwünschtes Unkraut]],name=[[Desert Rose]],class_level=26,help_en=[[Riding on the dry north winds out of the Black Shroud, kedtrap seeds have taken root in Thanalan. Without any natural predators, the seedkin are free to roam the desert unchecked, consuming everything in their path. The creatures must be tended to before they render the desert even more deserted than it already is!]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[妖花前線]],},[412]={name_fr=[[Le Prix De L'eau]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Sicherung Der Wasserversorgung]],name=[[Almost Paradise]],class_level=17,help_en=[[Anyone who has been to Drybone can easily see how the place earned its name. It is an unforgiving place─arid and dry beyond compare. What little water can be found in the area is so prized, men have been known to trade gold just for a sip. This is why the few springs must be protected from those who would foul them─slugs.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[楽園の泉]],},[413]={name_fr=[[Les Longues-cornes Se Cachent Pour Mourir]],class_level_max=22,name_de=[[Hörner Sind Zum Stutzen Da]],name=[[Deep In The Heart Of Sagolii]],class_level=17,help_en=[[Elder longhorns are extremely territorial and will attack anything which draws too close to their dens. This is fine when those dens are at the top of unscalable peaks, but when they lie within earshot of well-traveled caravan roads, things can become quite hairy. Drive the goats back to the mountains where they belong.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[長角の古老「エルダー・ロングホーン」]],},[419]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mise à Mort]],class_level_max=33,name_de=[[Miluda Die Schlitzerin]],name=[[Adventures In Throat Slitting]],class_level=28,help_en=[[The leader of the ill-famed Corpse Brigade, Milleuda the Slitter, has finally emerged from hiding to lead her men on a raid into the nearby hills. Use the opportunity to slay the killer and bring an end to her bloody reign.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[骸の頭目「流転のミルウーダ」]],},[420]={name_fr=[[Adieu Les Pots-de-vin]],class_level_max=32,name_de=[[Gefallene Helden]],name=[[The Corpse Bribe]],class_level=27,help_en=[[Once an arm of the proud Ala Mhigan army, the Corpse Brigade has devolved into a band of bandits and petty thieves, albeit well-trained ones. Several of the former soldiers earn their keep by setting up illegal roadblocks and demanding coin for passage. Show the curs that the sultana will not allow such acts under her rule.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[スープに肉を入れるため]],},[421]={name_fr=[[Odeur Alléchante]],class_level_max=30,name_de=[[Verteidigung Von Klein-Ala Mhigo]],name=[[Downwind]],class_level=25,help_en=[[A pack of violent sandskin peistes has been drawn to Little Ala Mhigo by the stench of the latrine pits which surround the mesa caves the Ala Mhigan refugees call home. While many of the settlers can hold their own in a fight, the sheer number of peistes may prove too much for the encampment.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[リトルアラミゴ防衛戦]],},[422]={name_fr=[[Tout Pour L'âme]],class_level_max=34,name_de=[[Marmor, Stein Und Eisen Brechen]],name=[[Soul Man]],class_level=29,help_en=[[A naturalist from Ul'dah is seeking to discover the secrets behind the force animating the silent stone creatures guarding the ruins at the Sunken Temple of Qarn, and will pay good gil for each soulstone extracted from the hearts of the golems.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[真理を解き明かせ]],},[423]={name_fr=[[Défi: Attention, Aspidochélon Méchant]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Kröte Mit Eisernem Schild]],name=[[Bigger Than Life]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Naturalists claim that it can take almost four score summers for an adamantoise to grow to full size. If that is to be believed, then one can only imagine how many summers it took for Aspidochelone to achieve its colossal mass...or how much it had to consume.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[大らかな圧殺者「アスピドケロン」]],},[424]={name_fr=[[Protéger Ses Arrières]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Hauptbrigadier Für Einen Tag]],name=[[Heroes Of The 2nd]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The Immortal Flames 2nd Main Brigade is moving to assault an Amalj'aa strongpoint and seeks reinforcements to help prevent its ranks from being flanked by the enemy.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[我ら第二戦闘大隊]],},[427]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Meilleure Défense...]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Auf Der Abschussliste]],name=[[Diamond In The Rough]],class_level=48,help_en=[[A great Ul'dahn general once said, “There is no need for defense when one is always on the offensive.” Assault the Zanr'ak encampment and slay the commanding officer Diamondjaw Nezedd Gah before he gathers his troops to march on Little Ala Mhigo.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[怒濤の怪力「金剛のネゼド・ガー」]],},[429]={name_fr=[[Enfants Des Sables]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Die Kinder Der Wüste]],name=[[Children Of The Sands]],class_level=31,help_en=[[The U tribe of Forgotten Springs, also known as the Children of the Sands, has gathered for the hunt. Join the savage beauties as they test their mettle against the giant sandworms of the Sagolii.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[砂漠の子供たち]],},[430]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sombre Futur Pour Le Voyant]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Schwarze Zukunft]],name=[[Return To Cinder]],class_level=49,help_en=[[The Zanr'ak altar is used to augur the outcome of future battles between the Amalj'aa and Ul'dah, and it is Cindersoot Pegujj Chah who throws the bones. Slay the mesmerizer and see that his fortune-telling days come to a bloody end.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[運命の代弁者「黒煙のペグジ・チャー」]],},[431]={name_fr=[[Chasser Ou être Chassé]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Kein Nachschub Für Zanr'ak]],name=[[Hunters And The Hunted]],class_level=49,help_en=[[A party of Amalj'aa warriors has gone foraging into Ul'dahn territory, raiding granaries and claiming livestock. Intercept the beastmen and beat them back to their mountain stronghold.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[狩る者と狩られる者]],},[432]={name_fr=[[Escorte Culturelle]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Begleitschutz]],name=[[From Point A]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Relics uncovered from the ruins at Byregot's Strike must first be cataloged in Forgotten Springs before being delivered to Arrzaneth Ossuary for further study. Escort the Stone Torch tasked with transporting the items from the dig site to the oasis, and see that she arrives safely.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[工神ビエルゴの守護者]],},[434]={name_fr=[[Course-poursuite Mortelle]],class_level_max=31,name_de=[[Der Kundschafter Und Seine Unerwünschte Kundschaft]],name=[[Run Like A Flame]],class_level=26,help_en=[[A flame scout caught spying on the Amalj'aa in Zanr'ak has escaped his captors and is making way to the aetheryte in Little Ala Mhigo, so that he may relay his findings to the Hall of Flames. The Amalj'aa, however, are in close pursuit and will do anything to see that their secrets remain hidden. Protect the scout at all costs!]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[偵察兵の仕事]],},[436]={name_fr=[[Défi: Une Magie Maléfique]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Der Gift Und Galle Spuckt]],name=[[Blood, Augur, Hex, Magicks]],class_level=32,help_en=[[The Immortal Flames have pinpointed the whereabouts of one Blackbile Maladd Chah─an Amalj'aa hexweaver thought to be behind the assassinations of several high-ranking flame officials. Track down the terrible warlock and send him back to the Lifestream.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[無道の暗殺者「呪言のマラド・チャー」]],},[437]={name_fr=[[Mise En Ordre]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Mehr Strand Als Meer]],name=[[Fish Out Of Water]],class_level=31,help_en=[[During the Calamity, the land's aetherial balance was disturbed─the result being a myriad of unexplained phenomena which has botanists and naturalists puzzled. What the scholars can agree on, however, is that the balance must be restored, and that means eradicating the problems as they emerge─and anglers in the desert certainly can be classified as one of those problems.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[流れる砂の海]],},[441]={name_fr=[[Survie Du Plus Apte]],class_level_max=33,name_de=[[Ein Maulkorb Für Kampf-Drakons]],name=[[Harder, Bigger, Faster, Stronger]],class_level=28,help_en=[[After years of experimentation, Amalj'aa beast tamers have finally perfected a new breed of biologically augmented drakes and have moved to testing the creatures in the field. Use this opportunity to slay the war creatures before they are taken back to their cages.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[まるで我が子の様に]],},[446]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Borgne Ravisseur]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Arimaspi-Alarm]],name=[[With One Eye Open]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Since the Calamity, the workers of Bluefog have told stories of a terrible one-eyed creature who would come in the night to carry sleeping men away from their campfires, never to be seen again. No one believed them...until a high-ranking Ul'dahn noble was snatched from his caravan. Now the city-state wants this Arimaspi's blinker on a pike.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[虚像の眼「アリマスピ」]],},[447]={name_fr=[[Basilics Illicites]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Erdseim Geht Vor]],name=[[Under The Nails]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Plans to expand the Ceruleum Processing Plant are in motion, with the next step being to clear the nearby land of the massive crystal protrusions known as Dalamud's Talons. To do that, however, the area must first be rid of the hostile basilisks who hunt there.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[爪切り]],},[449]={name_fr=[[Le Feu Aux Poudres]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Brandschutzmaßnahmen]],name=[[Boom Goes The Ceruleum]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Ceruleum is a highly flammable substance, and even the tiniest of sparks could cause an explosion, which is why the Ceruleum Processing Plant in Bluefog is especially wary of voidsent grenades straying too near the storage and rendering tanks.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[火の用心]],},[450]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Drone De Fer]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Der Erste Wird Der Letzte Sein]],name=[[Knock On Steel]],class_level=49,help_en=[[The imperial army's mad engineers have developed a new grade of armor plating for their warmachina and are already testing it out on their magitek vanguards. If the Grand Companies of Eorzea are to stand against the Empire, they must know the extent of Garlemald's defenses; thus, they seek adventurers to test their weapons on these mechanical beasts.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[新装甲採用機「魔導ヴァンガード試験型」]],},[451]={name_fr=[[Pauvre Hameau: Des Rats Qui Grignotent]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Köter Gegen Ratten]],name=[[Poor Maid's Mess]],class_level=20,help_en=[[Most likely assuming that there would still be poor maids living there, former-pirates-turned-model-citizens have exchanged their cutlasses for brooms and hammers in an effort to restore Poor Maid's Mill to its former pre-Calamity glory. Aid the men and women in clearing the farmstead of rats who now infest the ruins.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[プアメイドミル復興：食料防衛]],},[452]={name_fr=[[Pauvre Hameau: Des Kobolds Qui Saccagent]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Ungebetene Gäste]],name=[[Poor Maid's Mishap]],class_level=20,help_en=[[A band of kobolds led by 382nd Order Pickman Ge Bu has descended on Poor Maid's Mill in search of food and supplies. Aid the Salthounds in driving back the beastmen and defeating their commander.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[プアメイドミル復興：ゲ・ブ排撃]],},[453]={name_fr=[[Pauvre Hameau: Des Coeurls Qui Battent]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Vorsicht Bissig]],name=[[Poor Maid's Misfortune]],class_level=20,help_en=[[The Salthounds looking to restore Poor Maid's Mill cannot seem to catch a break, as now a pack of bloodthirsty coeurls has surrounded the ruins and has already dragged a few of the injured boatswains off into the wood. Join hands with the former pirates as they attempt to defend their little piece of La Noscea.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[プアメイドミル復興：クァール討伐]],},[454]={name_fr=[[Pauvre Hameau: Des Buffles Qui Piétinent]],class_level_max=25,name_de=[[Büffeln Statt Büffel]],name=[[Poor Maid's Misadventure]],class_level=20,help_en=[[If it isn't diseased rats, thieving kobolds, or bloodthirsty coeurls threatening to undo all the Salthounds have accomplished at Poor Maid's Mill, it's frenzied buffaloes looking to stomp the old farmstead into oblivion. Join with the former pirates one last time to see that all their efforts weren't for naught.]],name_ja=[[プアメイドミル復興：野牛討伐]],},[455]={name_fr=[[La Revanche Des Vers]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Wir Sind Gewurmt]],name=[[Revenge Of The Worms]],class_level=32,help_en=[[At a glance, sandworms seem little more than mindless minions of the desert, but it is now believed that each worm is bound to the others in their community, forming a sort of “hive mind” which recognizes when one part of the group has been injured or killed. This hive mind is now guiding a swarm of the worms towards Forgotten Springs to exact revenge on the U tribe.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[砂漠の神皇帝「ウルハドシ」]],},[456]={name_fr=[[Défi: Exécution Sommaire]],class_level_max=33,name_de=[[Buße Sollst Du Tun]],name=[[Bump And Grind]],class_level=28,help_en=[[The Brass Blades seek volunteers to aid them in the capture or slaying of Corpse Brigade captain Gisfrid the Grinder.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[持たざる者「破戒のギスフリッド」]],},[457]={name_fr=[[Ingénierie Inversée]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Reverse Engineering]],name=[[Reverse Engineering]],class_level=49,help_en=[[An engineering expert employed by Amajina & Sons seeks to uncover the secrets of the ceruleum engines which breathe life into the Empire's warmachina and will pay good coin for any engine parts brought back to him, regardless of their condition.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[リバースエンジニアリング]],},[460]={name_fr=[[Un Loup Pour L'homme]],class_level_max=40,name_de=[[Wer Fürchtet Sich]],name=[[Twelve Ilms Of Snow]],class_level=35,help_en=[[A pack of starving snow wolves has descended from its hunting grounds on the Nail to prey upon those who reside in and around the Observatorium. Drive the pack back to the mountains before there are any more casualties.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[白狼たちの戦旗]],},[463]={name_fr=[[Défi: Tondre Le Mouton Noir]],class_level_max=41,name_de=[[Pech Für Schwarze Schafe]],name=[[Baa Baa Black Sheep]],class_level=36,help_en=[[A legend amongst local Coerthan shepherds, Downy Dunstan is said to have wool as black as night and as soft as cloud. The problem is, most are never able to get close enough to the sheep to shear him properly, and those who are usually end up sacrificing a finger or two in the attempt. If someone were to pacify the beast, there would surely be those who would pay generously.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[黒き弾丸「ダウニーダンスタン」]],},[464]={name_fr=[[Défi: Cric, Crac, Croc!]],class_level_max=40,name_de=[[Gaviator - Tag Der Abrechnung]],name=[[Gavial]],class_level=35,help_en=[[Nobles and their pets. One day they will see some tiny creature from the window of their pillowed carriage and simply have to have it...that is, until it grows too large and violent for their quaint seaside villa, at which time they order their majordomo to toss it back into the wild, it now having learned to loathe all who might take advantage of it once again, until it finally has to be put down.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[川辺の復讐者「ガビアル」]],},[465]={name_fr=[[Conte D'hiver]],class_level_max=41,name_de=[[Hart Ist Der Winter]],name=[[Whiteout]],class_level=36,help_en=[[A blinding snowstorm on Abalathia's Spine has caused a pack of goobbues to lose its way and wander down into the more heavily populated areas of the Coerthas highlands. The creatures have already begun feeding on the locals' stock, and if not dealt with soon, there will be nothing left with which to survive the coming winter.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[冬物語]],},[466]={name_fr=[[Prier Sa Bonne étoile]],class_level_max=40,name_de=[[Astrologische Aufzeichnungen]],name=[[A Log Up]],class_level=35,help_en=[[The Dravanian Horde launched a brutal assault on the Observatorium just as her astrologians began moving this moon's astroscope logs to the lower library. Adventurers are needed to fend off the attack while protecting the scattered logs from the thrustaevis's all-consuming flames.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[星に願いを]],},[467]={name_fr=[[Imbroglio Avec Crocos]],class_level_max=41,name_de=[[Domigator-Dompteur]],name=[[Croc-y Road]],class_level=36,help_en=[[A porter on his way to Camp Dragonhead has had his way blocked by a bask of feral crocs. He doesn't dare stray too far from Haldrath's March for fear of being assaulted in the wild, but unless the crocs are dealt with, he will be unable to proceed to his destination.]],name_ja=[[ワイルドダイルダンディー]],},[469]={name_fr=[[Dans La Gueule Du Piège]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Wölfe Wittern Blut]],name=[[The Grey]],class_level=38,help_en=[[Since getting his leg caught in an iron trap, a sentry of House Fortemps has been tracked by a pack of wolves following the scent of his blood. The pack is right on his heels and without aid, he will not make it back to Ishgard alive.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[クルザスの白狼]],},[470]={name_fr=[[Pillards à Corne Rouge]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Nichts Da]],name=[[Simply Red]],class_level=38,help_en=[[A party of redhorn ogres has left its mountain lair to raid the smallfolk villages. It is not enough that they steal their food, but they kidnap their women and children as well. The poor farmers have no means of stopping these voidsent creatures, their fate balanced on the kindness of strangers.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[動く要塞]],},[472]={name_fr=[[La Source Des Ennuis]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Wertschöpfung]],name=[[Spring Forward, Fall Back]],class_level=38,help_en=[[A Coerthan merchant come to the Weeping Saint to collect holy water has found the spring guarded by mischievous sprites. Not willing to return to Ishgard empty-handed, he is offering to purchase any phials filled from the pool.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[流れよ我が涙]],},[473]={name_fr=[[Le Comble De La Crevasse]],class_level_max=42,name_de=[[Irregeleitet]],name=[[A Fire In The Distance]],class_level=37,help_en=[[Nothing is worse than being caught in a snowstorm at night than being caught in a snowstorm at night and falling into a bottomless ravine because you thought you spied a lantern in the distance...which actually turned out to be a will-o'-the-wisp. The wisps must be slain, for the safety of travelers throughout the realm.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[歓喜、慚愧、猛吹雪]],},[474]={name_fr=[[Ici Sont Les Dragons]],class_level_max=42,name_de=[[Drachenbelagerung]],name=[[Coming To A Head]],class_level=37,help_en=[[The Dravanian Horde has begun surrounding Camp Dragonhead. The knights stationed at the outpost seek aid in driving back the scalekin, for they do not believe their reinforcements from Ishgard will arrive in time.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[エイビスキラー]],},[475]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dans La Gamelle De Gargamelle]],class_level_max=44,name_de=[[Schluss Mit Gargamelle]],name=[[Bellyful]],class_level=39,help_en=[[A ferocious fiend named Gargamelle, rumored to have devoured twelve sick orphans being carried to the Warmwine Sanitorium for treatment, has been spotted hiding in an ice cave known as the Ogre's Belly. Put a blade through its black heart before it can claim any more innocent victims.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[大口の悪鬼「ガルガメル」]],},[479]={name_fr=[[Défi: Glacial Et Mortel]],class_level_max=44,name_de=[[Exergoninduzierte Eiszeit]],name=[[A Freeze Is Coming]],class_level=39,help_en=[[The fall of Dalamud brought an endless winter to the hills of Coerthas, and with the cold there came creatures of pure ice whose mere existence further rimes the land. Lutin is one of those creatures.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[凍てつく波動「リュタン」]],},[480]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Dernier Jour De Seps]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Schuppe Um Schuppe]],name=[[Giant Seps]],class_level=40,help_en=[[Many fine Ishgardian knights have fallen to the Dravanian Horde, but one dragon in particular has claimed more lives than most─its name, Seps. The winged aberration must be slain if the souls of its victims are to rest in peace.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[騎兵の天敵「セプス」]],},[482]={name_fr=[[Savoir Asséner La Bonne Réponse]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Riesenumweg]],name=[[Riddle Me This]],class_level=40,help_en=[[Giants demanding answers to their riddles three are preventing a party of naturalists from returning to Snowcloak. The problem is that even though the naturalists─learned men and women by trade─(somewhat) correctly answered all three riddles, the giants still refuse to let them pass. The only remaining solution is clear─answer the riddles with steel.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[血と肉の街道舗装]],},[483]={name_fr=[[Le Dernier Rempart Du Jugement]],class_level_max=44,name_de=[[Drachenfliegen]],name=[[Judge, Jury, And Executioner]],class_level=39,help_en=[[Dragonflies of the Dravanian Horde have gathered before Ishgard's final line of land defense─the Gates of Judgement. If the bastion is compromised, the Horde's wingless ground troops will gain entry to the city-state and thousands of lives will be lost. The gates must be defended at all costs.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[引き起こされた戦争]],},[484]={name_fr=[[Défi: Périlleuse Pérégrination]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Pilger In Gefahr]],name=[[In The Saint's Wake]],class_level=45,help_en=[[Every year, pilgrims enter Coerthas to trace the steps of Saint Daniffen, who, long ago, journeyed across the realm, aiding the less fortunate. And, every year, a lustful creature known as Rongeur hides in the shadows along the roads to prey on these pilgrims.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[骨貪る者「ロンジュール」]],},[486]={name_fr=[[Un Giga Problème]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Der Wille Von Haillenarte]],name=[[Tower Of Power]],class_level=45,help_en=[[As if Ishgard already did not have its hands full with the Dravanian Horde, hostile bands of giants from the north have also descended on Coerthas to wreak their havoc. House Haillenarte guards seek assistance in driving one such band from the area surrounding Monument Tower.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[アインハルトの意地]],},[487]={name_fr=[[Durendaire Dur à Cuire]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Auf Der Suche Nach Wärme]],name=[[Turn Off Your Hearthlight]],class_level=47,help_en=[[Giants in search of fire to cook their prey have begun a chaotic march toward the hearths within the Observatorium. Join the House Durendaire guards in repelling the onslaught.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[暖を求めて]],},[489]={name_fr=[[Ce Qui Vient Du Néant Doit Y Repartir]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Zerstreuung Für Pilger]],name=[[What's On Your Mind]],class_level=47,help_en=[[Very little is known about the void other than that the laws that govern our realm do not always apply. In addition to one-eyed monstrosities, peculiar balls of fur, and nightmarish demons, oddities such as floating orbs of energy also periodically break through the boundaries that separate this realm from the void. Make no mistake, however, everything through those rifts does not belong in Eorzea and must be destroyed.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[巡礼の道]],},[490]={name_fr=[[Défi: Que Ferait Un Géant Sans Son Chef?]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Kein Sieg Für Klythios]],name=[[The Bigger They Are]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Klythios, a leader and champion amongst the giants, has been spotted in the Coerthas highlands. If he is defeated, his dull-witted brethren are certain to think twice before venturing too deep into Ishgardian territory. Find the colossal warrior and send him toppling.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[愚鈍なる勇者「クリュティオス」]],},[491]={name_fr=[[Ce Que Disent Les étoiles]],class_level_max=41,name_de=[[Horoskop Für Drachenkopf]],name=[[Wish Upon A Star]],class_level=36,help_en=[[The previous evening's star readings are complete, and an astrologian from the Observatorium seeks well-armed adventurers to escort him as he delivers the findings to a courier at Camp Dragonhead, who will take them into Ishgard.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[星の光、今は遠く]],},[493]={name_fr=[[Défi: Se Battre Sobek Et Ongles]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Späte Vergeltung]],name=[[The Taste Of Fear]],class_level=40,help_en=[[Since breaking its way into one of the Skyfire Locks and devouring an entire family of refugees as they escaped the flames of the Dravanian Horde, the horrible scalekin Sebek has been sought by the knights of Ishgard to pay for its heinous crimes.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[雪山の襲撃者「セベク」]],},[494]={name_fr=[[Défi: Volatile Pêcheur]],class_level_max=44,name_de=[[Rotgeflügelter Roc]],name=[[Roc Of Ages]],class_level=39,help_en=[[Skyfishing is the sole means of survival for countless Ishgardian skyfishers, the strange denizens of the Sea of Clouds crucial to maintaining the fishers' livelihoods. This is why when a giant bird with a seemingly insatiable appetite appears and begins devouring them all, the skyfishers take notice.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[赤い翼「ロック」]],},[496]={name_fr=[[Qu'ils S'arrêtent à L'Arête]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Auf Ruf Der Drachen]],name=[[Front And Center]],class_level=40,help_en=[[The Dravanian elders have ordered their minions to attack Whitebrim Front. Hold the line until Ishgardian reinforcements arrive or the elders sound the retreat.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[それは竜の意思！]],},[497]={name_fr=[[Élémentaires à Congeler]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Abtauen]],name=[[If This Wall Could Talk]],class_level=40,help_en=[[With a team of naturalists from across the realm working day and night to discover the origins of Snowcloak and how it might be destroyed, there is one thing they have uncovered─that energy from ice sprites actually works to increase the thickness of the wall. The research team seeks volunteers to clear the area of the pesky sprites.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[氷づけになるがいい！]],},[498]={name_fr=[[Déforestation Sauvage]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Gestohlen Gut]],name=[[Does Anyone Hear It]],class_level=48,help_en=[[The Ixal are looking to expand their settlement of Natalan and have begun clear-cutting the nearby forests for wood. Infiltrate Natalan and destroy the lumber so as to slow the expansion's progress.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[入植を阻止せよ]],},[499]={name_fr=[[Défi: Les Quatre Sœurs Du Malheur]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Wilde Schwestern]],name=[[The Four Winds]],class_level=49,help_en=[[The four sisters of the Hueloc high clan are feared even by their fellow Ixal for the lack of mercy they show their victims. Though it would be doing the beast tribe a favor, it will not only be the Ixal who benefit from the slaying of the Huelocs.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[烈風の勇士「フェロック四姉妹」]],},[500]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Tronçonneur]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Kein Holz Für Natalan]],name=[[Inspector Hatchet]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Gozol Itzcan the Hatchet is infamous for his endless raids into the Twelveswood to fell ancient sentinels. Track down the feathered fiend while he is perched in Natalan, and see that he never swings an axe again.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[匠の技「工匠のゴゾル・イツカン」]],},[501]={name_fr=[[Svara S'en Est Venu: Dragon En Vue]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Wettlauf Gegen Svara]],name=[[Svara's Flight]],class_level=38,help_en=[[The Observatorium reports that the dragon Svara has been seen flying in the direction of the Steel Vigil. Protect the engineer moving into position to ready the siege machine.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[スヴァラ迎撃作戦：工兵護送]],},[502]={name_fr=[[Svara S'en Est Venu: Le Siège]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Kanone Gegen Svara]],name=[[Svara's Fear]],class_level=38,help_en=[[The engineer is in position and has begun readying the dragonslayer cannons; however, deadly threats approach from all sides. Fend off the encroaching horde so that the engineer can finish his preparations.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[スヴァラ迎撃作戦：砲撃準備]],},[503]={name_fr=[[Svara S'en Est Venu: Les Canons Anti-dragon]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Feuer Frei Auf Svara]],name=[[Svara's Fall]],class_level=38,help_en=[[The mighty dragon Svara has landed and begun its relentless attack on the Ishgardian defenses. Fight alongside Bertha to turn the tide of battle in your favor.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[スヴァラ迎撃作戦：砲撃応戦]],},[504]={name_fr=[[Svara S'en Est Venu: La Colère Du Dragon]],class_level_max=43,name_de=[[Wehrlos Vor Svara]],name=[[Svara's Fury]],class_level=38,help_en=[[The mighty dragon Svara has landed and begun its relentless attack on the Ishgardian defenses. The cannon that was meant to aid the Ishgardian forces, however, has been destroyed. It appears your blades are the only thing that can prevent utter defeat this day.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[スヴァラ迎撃作戦：人海戦術]],},[505]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'ire Du Béhémoth]],class_level_max=255,name_de=[[Der Legendäre Behemoth]],name=[[Behold Now Behemoth]],class_level=50,help_en=[[The legendary behemoth has left its mountaintop dominion to hunt...and we are his prey. Gather your blades and your wits and pray to the Twelve for strength, for you will need it to quell the beast's infinite rage.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[伝説の魔獣「ベヒーモス」]],},[506]={name_fr=[[Défi: Contre-traque]],class_level_max=255,name_de=[[Kein Weg Zurück]],name=[[He Taketh It With His Eyes]],class_level=50,help_en=[[The behemoth has taken flight back to its dominion. Make chase and finish the legendary beast once and for all.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[手負いの魔獣「ベヒーモス」]],},[507]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'œil De La Tête]],class_level_max=44,name_de=[[Mehr Augen, Mehr Ärger]],name=[[The Eyes Have It]],class_level=39,help_en=[[After proving his might on the shores of Turtleback Island, the cyclops Steropes has returned to Eorzea, but this time with a personal army of giants who call themselves the Second Eyes. Defeat Steropes before he can cause any real damage.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[帰ってきた男「ステロペス」]],},[508]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Prophète Du Vent]],class_level_max=52,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Beschwörer Der Herrin Der Winde]],name=[[The Storm Caller]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Kozol Nomotl the Turbulent, chief among the rank of Ixali occultists, has come to Natalan to personally preside over the summoning of the primal Garuda. Slay the Ixal that the land might be spared a stormy fate.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[嵐神呼びし者「風標のコゾル・ノモトル」]],},[512]={name_fr=[[Des Crapauds En Trop]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Aus Kameradschaft]],name=[[Toll Collector]],class_level=45,help_en=[[An adventurer returned to Camp Revenant's Toll to see if she could locate items abandoned there five years past has found the site overrun with poisonous gigantoads. She seeks assistance in clearing away the wavekin.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[失われた風景]],},[514]={name_fr=[[Enchevêtrement Fatal]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Großreinemachen Im Schlingwald]],name=[[Mud About You]],class_level=44,help_en=[[The endless maze of roots and trees already creates enough trouble for those travelers who brave the Tangle; the last thing any of them want to think upon is how to fend off a pack of hungry mudpuppies. Clear the waters of these wavekin, but ware the morbols lurking nearby.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[タングル湿林の大掃除]],},[516]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sonner Le Glas Pour Nburu]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Nburus Bitterkeit]],name=[[Black And Nburu]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The adventurers of Revenant's Toll whisper rumors of a long-dead spirit who is damned to roam the Tangle for eternity, preying on the souls of the living out of pure spite─his name, Nburu.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[湿林の怨念「ンブル」]],},[517]={name_fr=[[Trop De Morbols Tuent Les Morbols]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Ausgekeimt]],name=[[Good To Be Bud]],class_level=44,help_en=[[When a morbol begins to bud, it can only mean one thing─more morbols. The realm does not need any more morbols.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[モルボル怒りの大増殖]],},[520]={name_fr=[[Ces Tests Doivent échouer]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Wartung Aller Waffen]],name=[[Standing Guard]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Garlean engineers are constantly at work modifying and improving the design of their machina. A new make of vanguard, the H-3, has recently been deployed into the field for testing. Destroy them and stall the march of imperial progress.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[統合整備計画]],},[521]={name_fr=[[Défi: Porus Et Les 1000 Chasseurs]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Nichts Geht Mehr]],name=[[Another Notch On The Torch]],class_level=48,help_en=[[Gorer of a thousand guts, Porus of the redhorns has taken refuge in the Singing Shards after being pursued halfway across Coerthas by a band of bounty hunters─the bounty hunters his 997th, 998th, 999th, and 1000th victims. See that you aren't his 1001st.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[残忍なる悪鬼「ポリュス」]],},[522]={name_fr=[[Chacun Sa Terre Sainte]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Umkämpfter Kristallturm]],name=[[One Giant Leap]],class_level=46,help_en=[[It has recently been discovered in ancient Sharlayan documents that the gigas believe the Crystal Tower a holy place, and that is the reason why the colossal beings have begun gathering in north Silvertear. This, unfortunately, has made it difficult for the Sons of Saint Coinach to conduct their research, what with the gigas constantly destroying their findings.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[聖地巡礼]],},[523]={name_fr=[[Sus Aux Gigas]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Hände Weg Von Geisterzoll]],name=[[Among Giants]],class_level=45,help_en=[[Driven south by the cold weather and lack of prey, many gigas have taken a foothold on the northern shore of Silvertear Lake, much to the chagrin of the Sons of Saint Coinach who are currently in the area studying the ancient ruins and crystalline phenomena. The Sons seek assistance in driving the colossi from the area.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[巨漢の地上げ屋]],},[524]={name_fr=[[À Chaque Jour Suffit Son Monstre]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Hippogryhpen Greifen An]],name=[[Another Day, Another Demon]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Most only simple naturalists─their wits the sharpest weapon in their packs─the Sons of Saint Coinach are finding it difficult to carry out their research when it seems like every day they are being hunted by some pack of mythical wild beasts. Today's excitement─a flock of hungry hippogryphs.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[ヒッポグリフの晩餐会]],},[525]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dioné-nous La Force]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Dione Muss Schweigen]],name=[[That's What Adventurers Are For]],class_level=46,help_en=[[The Sons of Saint Coinach find themselves in a bind once again, this time thanks to one Dione─a gigas high priest rumored to be older than time itself. The naturalists won't sleep easy until this menace is resting at the bottom of Silvertear Lake.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[乱れ髪「銀髪のディオネ」]],},[526]={name_fr=[[Pas Les Bienvenus]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Die Hapaliten Sind Los]],name=[[Home Is Where The Horn Is]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Hapalits, foul cousins of the ogres, are on the move in search of a new lair, far from the levinbolts of their former abode. The violent creatures have a natural tendency to tear anything moving into two, and so while one might sympathize with their plight to find a new home, it is for the best that they are not allowed to set up camp anywhere nearby.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[銀泪湖ガラガラドッカン]],},[527]={name_fr=[[Défi: En Proie Aux Ombres]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Recht Gilt Auch Des Nachts]],name=[[Gone With The Shadow]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Over the course of the past three nights, three Sons of Saint Coinach have gone missing from their tents. The guards claim they saw nothing but shadows, but perhaps therein lies the answer to this mystery. Let the dark hunt begin!]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[夜襲の魔獣「グウィルギ」]],},[529]={name_fr=[[Une Escorte Pour La Science]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Forsch Und Forscher]],name=[[The Prodigal Son]],class_level=45,help_en=[[One of the Sons of Saint Coinach requires an escort deep into dangerous territory so that he may continue his research on the acoustic properties of the aetherial manifestations of the area.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[旅の仲間]],},[530]={name_fr=[[Défi: Parfum Trompeur]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Hab Vivian Satt]],name=[[V For Vinedetta]],class_level=44,help_en=[[More than one weary adventurer has wandered into the Tangle, lured by the sweet smell of a noblewoman's perfume, only to find the gaping maw of Voluptuous Vivian─a massive morbol with a taste for the flesh of man.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[甘い誘惑「ボラプチュア・ビビアン」]],},[532]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=37,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=32,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[533]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=5,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[534]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=18,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=13,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[535]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=5,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[536]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=20,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=15,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[537]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=16,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=11,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[538]={name_fr=[[Le Retour D'un Roi]],class_level_max=11,patch={number=[[2.0]],},name_de=[[Comeback Mit Knall]],name=[[Return Of The King]],class_level=6,help_en=[[After a five year absence, the Bombard King has appeared in Eorzea once again (much to the delight of the Cascadiers). Don your uniforms and head into battle with the cadets, protecting the brave men and women while they attempt to dispatch the royal pain.]],name_ja=[[帰ってきた大炎獣「キングボンバード」]],},[540]={name_fr=[[Quitte Ou Doblyn]],class_level_max=47,name_de=[[Dem Quarz Zuliebe]],name=[[Quartz Coupling]],class_level=42,help_en=[[After years of searching, doblyn breeding grounds have finally been discovered in eastern Thanalan. Now that we know where they mate, we can stop them from reproducing and save countless tonzes of ore from needless consumption.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ワサワサドブラン]],},[541]={name_fr=[[De L'autre Côté Du Miroir]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Angst Vor Dem Unbekannten]],name=[[A Man Rides Through]],class_level=40,help_en=[[A strange armored figure was recently seen emerging from a fallen piece of Dalamud. Proceed with caution. The creature could be hostile.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[鏡像の騎士]],},[542]={name_fr=[[Défi: Pelote En Colère]],class_level_max=47,name_de=[[Holder Knabe In Lockigem Haar]],name=[[Bad Hair Day]],class_level=42,help_en=[[Countless vials of snurble and phurble blood have transformed what was once a man into a mad tangle of golden fur. Put poor Aeetes out of his misery.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[金髪の貴公子「アイエテス」]],},[543]={name_fr=[[Défi: Se Forger Des Chimères]],class_level_max=47,name_de=[[Großer Badu, Große Gefahr]],name=[[The Big Bagoly Theory]],class_level=42,help_en=[[After showing absolutely no signs that they were any more than twisted masses of metal, debris fallen from Dalamud five summers past is coming to life and brutally attacking those unfortunate enough to come across the inorganic creatures. One of these “mirrorknights,” as the people call them, has been sighted destroying a farmstead nearby.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[醜悪なる合成獣「バドゥ」]],},[545]={name_fr=[[Le Feu Sacré]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Zeremonienverderber]],name=[[Call Me, Mayhaps]],class_level=46,help_en=[[A nearby party of Amalj'aa is attempting an Ifrit summoning. Slay the invokers and destroy the glowing cresset used in the rite before the primal's aether finishes gathering.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[荒野の消火活動]],},[546]={name_fr=[[Défi: Bibireze Le Maudit]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Ifrit Nahm Sein Leben]],name=[[Book Of Pride]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Bibireze Greysteel and his men believed they could defeat Ifrit. They were wrong, and their hubris cost them their minds. The tempered heroes now wander the deserts of southern Thanalan doing the Lord of the Inferno's bidding. Free these lost souls to the Lifestream.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[哀しき闘士「純鉄のビビレゼ」]],},[548]={name_fr=[[Feu Aux Poudres]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Ifrits Quell Der Kraft]],name=[[Tempered, Tempered]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Instead of killing his victims, Ifrit will “temper” them, burning away their wills, rendering them mindless servants to the Lord of the Inferno. As a primal is only as powerful as the number of its followers, returning the souls of the tempered to the Lifestream effectively weakens the demigods.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[正義についての話をしよう]],},[549]={name_fr=[[Le Maillon Faible]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Verwüsten Verboten]],name=[[Full Of Rigor Mortis]],class_level=46,help_en=[[To survive, an iron tortoise must consume three times its weight every sennight. These dining habits can put a tax on local foliage, and transform a lush oasis into a barren wasteland in a matter of moons. To prevent the further desertification of southern Thanalan, the iron tortoise population must be thinned.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[甲羅を蹴飛ばせ！]],},[550]={name_fr=[[La Horde De La Discorde]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Blutige Aussichten]],name=[[An Inconvenient Truth]],class_level=48,help_en=[[A unit of well-trained Amalj'aa known as the Gore Horde has been dispatched from their homeland Paglth'an with a single purpose─to lay waste to close-lying Ul'dahn settlements. Intercept the unit and wet the sands with beastman blood.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[精鋭部隊「ゴアホード」]],},[551]={name_fr=[[Horoscope Du Jour]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Kein Glückstag]],name=[[Future Shock]],class_level=48,help_en=[[An extremely superstitious lot, the Amalj'aa will, before every march into enemy territory, augur the outcome of the forthcoming battles at the Zanr'ak altar. These bloody ceremonies offer us an opportune time to strike the beastmen unawares. They will never see us coming...or will they!?]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[今日の運勢]],},[552]={name_fr=[[Que Décline Son Armée]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Geflüchtet Und Entführt]],name=[[Taken]],class_level=45,help_en=[[Several residents of Little Ala Mhigo have been abducted by a party of tempered servants of Ifrit. Slay the assailants and save the victims before the Lord of the Inferno adds new souls to his ever-growing army.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[友と、家族と]],},[553]={name_fr=[[Massacre Derrière La Herse]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Tumult Am Ersten Tor]],name=[[Gyve Talk]],class_level=49,help_en=[[The Amalj'aa of Zahar'ak have begun gathering troops outside the 1st Gyve in preparation for what can only be a march into Ul'dahn territory. Break their ranks and send the beastmen scattering.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[第一関門攻略戦]],},[554]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Hepugg à épurer]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Schneller Schütze]],name=[[Spark Off The Bench]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Whitespark Hepugg Roh─an eagle-eyed Amalj'aa archer with the strength to pierce three Immortal Flames with a single arrow─has been sighted lurking nearby. Hunt down the named fiend and see that his sharpshooting days are through.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[速射の名手「火打のハプグ・ロー」]],},[555]={name_fr=[[D'élégants Morts-vivants]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Fäulnis Mit Stil]],name=[[Fallen Corpses Writhe In Style]],class_level=46,help_en=[[A band of zombies has been exhibiting uncharacteristically civilized behavior of late, which has greatly unnerved the people of Thanalan. Dispatch the dapper undead for the benefit of the living.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[砂の上の足あと]],},[556]={name_fr=[[Ne Jetez Pas Les Noyaux !]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Erdkern Für Erdseim]],name=[[Core Blimey]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Ceruleum processing is a complex task that requires a stable environment so as not to disturb the highly unstable liquid. One way to reduce seismic activity in and around the plant is by reinforcing the area with earth sprite cores, and Amajina & Sons draughtsmen are always looking to purchase more.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[青燐精製所のお手伝い]],},[557]={name_fr=[[L'élite Des Crocs]],class_level_max=52,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Aufflammende Gewalt]],name=[[Quenching The Flame]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Members of the notorious Flamefang Amalj'aa have assembled in Zahar'ak in preparation for their next raid. Now is the time to strike a blow against these fanatical servants of Ifrit. Defeat the Flamefang commander and his elite minions.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[アマルジャ軍特殊部隊「炎牙衆」]],},[558]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'attiseur Des Flammes Infernales]],class_level_max=51,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Beschwörer Des Herrn Des Infernos]],name=[[He's A Firestarter]],class_level=48,help_en=[[Flamecrest Afajj Koh, one of Ifrit's foremost priests, has come to Zahar'ak to personally preside over the summoning of his lord. Eliminate the influential Amalj'aa, lest the land be given to the flames.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[焔神呼びし者「火印のアファジ・コー」]],},[560]={name_fr=[[L'insécurité De L'emploi]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Geld Oder Leben]],name=[[9 To 5]],class_level=32,help_en=[[After the Calamity devastated much of Eorzea's workforce, Mamool Ja mercenaries were called over from their homeland to do everything from slay aether-crazed monsters to tile rooves. However, now with the return of a much more stable workforce in adventurers, many of the Mamool Ja find themselves out of work...and have turned to banditry to make ends meet.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[野蛮な餓えた傭兵の反乱]],},[561]={name_fr=[[Défi: Alcool Triste]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Geschmack An Wein Und Unrecht]],name=[[Closing Time]],class_level=34,help_en=[[Some creatures crave blood, others treasure. But there is one fiend of the night who craves neither. What Sekhmet craves is wine, and he will cease at nothing to get his thieving claws on a bottle of fine grape, be it red or white. He will even go as far as killing a man...which is why he must now be stopped.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[酒飲み魔獣「セクメト」]],},[562]={name_fr=[[Entre Miel Et Terre]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Liebliche Weinblüten]],name=[[Sweeter Than Honey]],class_level=33,help_en=[[To attract more bees to pollinate the vineyard, one of the bonds has come up with the idea of applying sweet raincatcher nectar to the grape trestles, and now seeks volunteers to aid him in collecting the liquid from the giant flowers.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[蜜蜂誘う甘い蜜]],},[563]={name_fr=[[Défi: Ho, Ho, Ho!]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Glüxi Grün]],name=[[Ho Ho Ho]],class_level=33,help_en=[[Do not be fooled by his jovial laugh, for Jolly Green is aught but joyful. The overgrown goobbue will snatch up and swallow everything within his grasp, and this includes adventurers. Now is the time to turn his frown upside down.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[深緑の巨獣「ジョリーグリーン」]],},[564]={name_fr=[[Défi: Celui Dont On Ne Doit Pas Prononcer Le Nom]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Metshaldjas Von Rechts]],name=[[Say My Name]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Local legend states that he who calls the name of Metshaldjas three times will summon the unspeakable woodland monstrosity from deep beneath the earth to wield destruction on the world above. Fortunately, few can pronounce the name. Unfortunately, it appears someone was lucky.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[不吉な球根「メツハルジャス」]],},[565]={name_fr=[[Laissez-moi Rentrer Chez Moi !]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Nach Hause Teleportieren]],name=[[Long Way Home]],class_level=33,help_en=[[Slavering beasts block a wine porter's way back to the arms of his loving wife. Put a fear into the creatures so that the lonely lad and his libido can make it home.]],name_ja=[[お家に帰ろう]],},[566]={name_fr=[[Quand Le Liège Assiège]],class_level_max=37,name_de=[[Straßenverwüster]],name=[[Cliff Hanger]],class_level=32,help_en=[[Cork bulbs will often choose to set their roots deep in the side of cliffs to better protect themselves from hungry predators. This, unfortunately, is a major cause of landslides which block thoroughfares and claim the lives of countless chocobos. Seek out the bulbs and slay the seedkin before they can dig any deeper.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[球根つぶし]],},[568]={name_fr=[[Reconnaissance Au Barrage Du Nord]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Aufklärung Am Norddamm]],name=[[Gauging North Tidegate]],class_level=44,help_en=[[A party of Sahagin scouts has approached North Tidegate in an attempt to gauge the strength of its defenses. Drive the beastmen back to the sea.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[北防波壁の戦い：威力偵察]],},[569]={name_fr=[[Percée Du Barrage Du Nord]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Schlacht Am Norddamm]],name=[[Breaching North Tidegate]],class_level=44,help_en=[[A failed attempt by the garrison at North Tidegate to drive back a party of Sahagin scouts has emboldened the beastmen into launching an attempt to breach the massive wall. The Sahagin and their leader Meww the Pusher must not be allowed to pass at any cost.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[北防波壁の戦い：本隊強襲]],},[570]={name_fr=[[Reconnaissance Au Barrage Du Sud]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Aufklärung Am Süddamm]],name=[[Gauging South Tidegate]],class_level=45,help_en=[[A party of Sahagin scouts has approached South Tidegate in an attempt to gauge the strength of its defenses. Drive the beastmen back to the sea.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[南防波壁の戦い：威力偵察]],},[571]={name_fr=[[Percée Du Barrage Du Sud]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Schlacht Am Süddamm]],name=[[Breaching South Tidegate]],class_level=45,help_en=[[A failed attempt by the garrison at South Tidegate to drive back a party of Sahagin scouts has emboldened the beastmen into launching an attempt to breach the massive wall. The Sahagin and their leader Mouu the Puller must not be allowed to pass at any cost.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[南防波壁の戦い：本隊強襲]],},[572]={name_fr=[[Défi: Qui Veut La Peau Du Requin ?]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Voll Unter Kontrolle]],name=[[Sharknado]],class_level=44,help_en=[[High-ranking Sahagin official (if such a thing exists) Voll the Sharkskinned has arrived at Tidegate to observe the work of his subordinates. There will never be a better opportunity to take the known killer's head. Do not let him slip from our grasp!]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[冷徹なる戦略家「鮫肌のヴォル」]],},[574]={name_fr=[[La Tentation Du Serpent De Mer]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Von Der Schlange Verführt]],name=[[Tail Of A Whale]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Instead of killing his victims, the primal Leviathan will “drown” them, erasing their wills and rendering them mindless servants of the Lord of the Whorl. Sahagin leader Worr the Whalefin commands an army of these pitiless souls, and that army is on the move, looking for their master's next victims!]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[海蛇の末路]],},[575]={name_fr=[[Marquée De Votre Lame]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Oberschlange]],name=[[Watch Your Tongue]],class_level=48,help_en=[[Notorious Serpent Reaver captain Aermswys the Stained is believed to be hiding somewhere in the Serpent's Tongue. Hunt down the wanted criminal and send her to the abyss.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[海蛇の船長「刻印のエルムスイス」]],},[576]={name_fr=[[C'est Pas L'homme Qui Prend La Mer...]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Totengeleit]],name=[[Dead Man's Rest]],class_level=40,help_en=[[There are some sailors who, even after death, cannot bear to part from the sea, their moans a testament to the chains that bind them to the corporeal realm. Slay these wandering spirits and sever those bonds so that they may return to the Lifestream.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[死の行進]],},[577]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mante à L'eau]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Verhängnisvolle Fracht]],name=[[The King's Justice]],class_level=40,help_en=[[There are many creatures in Eorzea who call themselves “king”; however, only one of those is a mantis with claws powerful enough to decollate a stone golem─the mantis king. Stay on your toes, or it is off with your head.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[異国の魔蟲「マンティスキング」]],},[578]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Messager Des Vagues]],class_level_max=52,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Beschwörer Des Herrn Der Wogen]],name=[[Making Waves]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Yarr the Wavefiend, he who speaks with Leviathan's voice, has come to the Sapsa Spawning Grounds to see his lord resurrected. Suffice it to say he cannot be allowed to succeed. Slay him, and send his ambitions sinking to the briny depths.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[水神呼びし者「水鬼のヤァル」]],},[580]={name_fr=[[De Hauteur De Golem]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Basaltblockade]],name=[[The Only Way Is Up]],class_level=34,help_en=[[The long and winding road known as the Long Climb is one of only two means to reach Camp Overlook, and when this road is blocked by golems wielded by powerful warlocks looking to rob couriers and caravans, it is the residents of that camp who suffer. Defeat the basalt golems and ensure the safety of those who walk the Long Climb.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ザ・ロード]],},[581]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Coeurl à Prendre]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Für Unsere Pioniere]],name=[[By A Whisker]],class_level=34,help_en=[[It is not enough that he killed and devoured a total of twenty-seven of the original laborers sent to outer La Noscea to build Camp Overlook, but Ose─king among coeurls─is once again terrorizing the storm soldiers stationed at the remote outpost.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[黒渦団の仇敵「オセ」]],},[583]={name_fr=[[Hauts Les Coeurls]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Ein Prachtvoller Feind]],name=[[When The Coeurl's Away]],class_level=34,help_en=[[A pride of coeurls is roaming along the narrow mountain road leading to and from Camp Overlook, preying on anything that is foolish enough to pass their way. Defeat the beastkin and secure the road.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[豹よ、豹よ！]],},[586]={name_fr=[[Défi: Pas De Concession Sur Les Concessions]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Riecher Für Erz]],name=[[The Miner In The Mirror]],class_level=44,help_en=[[Be Ze─pickman of the 59th Order of kobolds and enemy of miners across La Noscea─is infamous for ruthlessly exploiting mineral deposits of all their resources, leaving them barren for all those who come to O'Ghomoro in search of ore. The greedy beastman must be taught a lesson that Hydaelyn's bounty is meant for all Her children.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[土竜の山師「ピックマン59 ベ・ゼ」]],},[587]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Kobold Sachant Forer...]],class_level_max=46,name_de=[[Gras Grüner, Gestein Größer]],name=[[Schism]],class_level=41,help_en=[[Under command by Matriarch Go Zu, the kobolds of the 59th Order have commenced drilling at their makeshift dig site. Impede their progress by destroying the kobolds' tools.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[試掘地強襲作戦]],},[588]={name_fr=[[Le Temps Est à La Grenade]],class_level_max=46,name_de=[[Granaten In Sicht]],name=[[Fire In The Hole]],class_level=41,help_en=[[Drawn by whatever it is that draws voidsent from their midnight realm to this one, a cloud of grenades slowly floats in the direction of Camp Overlook. If it were to arrive at the outpost, the results would be deadly; therefore the cloud must be diverted at once.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[ファイア・イン・ザ・ホール]],},[589]={name_fr=[[Défi: Peur De L'orage?]],class_level_max=46,name_de=[[Auf Wolkenbruch Raus]],name=[[Make It Rain]],class_level=41,help_en=[[Whether or not you believe the stories of Brounger─a mythical spirit said to conjure terrible storms in the heavens─it does not change the fact that currently in outer La Noscea roams a mythical spirit said to conjure terrible storms in the heavens.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[雷雨呼ぶ者「ブラウンガー」]],},[591]={name_fr=[[Défi: Qui A Vu Mon Dragon ?]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Ende Eines Gerüchts]],name=[[Peryton, Perhaps]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Recently, a grizzled old scout with a single rheumy eye returned from the Floating City of Nym claiming he had seen the shadow of a giant dragon land on one of the suspended isles. Now the entire region is crawling with would-be dragonslayers eager to claim the creature's hoard.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[伝説の巨竜「ペリュトン」]],},[593]={name_fr=[[Véloces Raptors]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Keine Fragen. Renn.]],name=[[Restless In O'Ghomoro]],class_level=34,help_en=[[Something further up O'Ghomoro has sent a pack of raptors into a frenzy, and now the restless scalekin threaten to injure the residents of Camp Overlook and beyond. Find the creatures and put them down.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[狂気の山脈]],},[594]={name_fr=[[Défi: Je Ne Suis Pas Un Numéro]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Fehlschöpfung]],name=[[I'm A Rock, Not A Number]],class_level=34,help_en=[[An ungodly experiment in creation gone wrong, Number 128 does not belong in this world. Hunt down the masterless golem and put an end to the abomination.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[廃棄された実験体「ナンバー128」]],},[595]={name_fr=[[Kobolds En Embuscade]],class_level_max=39,name_de=[[Ladenbesitzer In Not]],name=[[Overlooking The Obvious]],class_level=34,help_en=[[While escorting a carriage of supplies to Camp Overlook, a Maelstrom unit was ambushed by kobolds and slaughtered to the last man. Now, the lone remaining coachman scrambles to stay alive while awaiting rescue. Any and all assistance is welcome.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[補給部隊救出命令]],},[597]={name_fr=[[Défi: Révolution Industrielle]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Asbest? Nein Danke!]],name=[[Full Metal Alchemist]],class_level=48,help_en=[[59th Order Bedesman Bi Go is a skilled alchemist, known for his experimentations on coblyns. His research has led to vast improvements in kobold metallurgical techniques, which, in time, will lead to better kobold weapons, which, ultimately, will lead to more Maelstrom casualties. Locate the holy man and cease his advancements.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[鋼虫の養殖者「ビーズマン59 ビ・ゴ」]],},[598]={name_fr=[[Défi: Ne Pas Réveiller La Statue Qui Dort...]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Schlafende Monster]],name=[[Spandy Balidet]],class_level=47,help_en=[[In their incessant diggings, the kobolds have unearthed something that was better left buried─a living statue of a time long past, awoken from an eternity of slumber to kill once again.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[目覚めし石像「バリデト」]],},[599]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'allocutaire De La Roche]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Beschwörer Des Herrn Der Felsen]],name=[[Stopping The Shakes]],class_level=47,help_en=[[5th Order Patriarch Ze Bu, chosen of Titan, has come to U'Ghamaro Mines to personally preside over the summoning of his lord. See the kobold returned to the earth, else the land shall be made to tremble once more.]],map={placename={name=[[Outer La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[岩神呼びし者「ペイトリアーク05 ゼ・ブ」]],},[600]={name_fr=[[Mornes Lindwurms]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Wurmige Ernte]],name=[[The Lindwurm Has Turned]],class_level=31,help_en=[[A pair of lovers on their way home from Hopeseed Pond were brutally attacked by a pack of lindwurms drawn by the sweet smell of the day's catch. See the scalekin slain so that they can never harm another.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[強襲リンドヴルム]],},[601]={name_fr=[[Soigner Le Mal Par Le Mal]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Dosis Macht Gift]],name=[[What's Your Poison]],class_level=30,help_en=[[The Wood Wailers seek poisonous mushroom spores to create an antidote...for poisonous mushroom spores. They will purchase any brought to them, as long as the product is pure.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[とても楽しいキノコ狩り]],},[602]={name_fr=[[Départs]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Frieden Ihrer Seele]],name=[[Revenant Things]],class_level=31,help_en=[[Sometimes, people are unaware when the end knocks, and their souls miss the opportunity to journey back into the Lifestream. These wretched creatures are known as revenants, and they need your help in realizing there is no place for them in this realm.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[送り火と]],},[603]={name_fr=[[Un Golem, Comment ça Marche ?]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Geheimnis Des Lebens]],name=[[If I Only Had A Soul]],class_level=33,help_en=[[Many mysteries still surround golems and how the creatures are animated. Stillglade Fane seeks to unlock the secrets of the lithic creatures and require soulstones to do so.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[真理を求めて]],},[604]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Plus Revanchard Des Deux]],class_level_max=48,name_de=[[Schadenfröhlich]],name=[[In Spite Of It All]],class_level=43,help_en=[[Deep within the Twelveswood lives a spriggan with a heart blacker than his stygian shock of fur─his name, Spiteful. So filled with malice, this creature does not distinguish between friend or foe, mercilessly attacking any who cross his path. The elementals have spoken. Spiteful's time in the forest is done.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[陰険なる魔物「スパイトフル」]],},[607]={name_fr=[[Vivre Libre Ou Mourir]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Sylphenfreundschaft]],name=[[Collecting Keepsakes]],class_level=40,help_en=[[Dear friends of Phanaxio of the New Leaf were killed by a band of sylphs for refusing to join them in their summoning of the primal Ramuh. Though he knows there is naught that will bring his companions back, he seeks their effects, so that their memories may endure.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[過ぎ去りし日々の光]],},[608]={name_fr=[[Occlusion D'otyughs]],class_level_max=45,name_de=[[Grenzschutz]],name=[[All Vine And No Popotoes]],class_level=40,help_en=[[Ochus released into the forest by sylphs to act as deterrents to those seeking entry into their homeland have begun wandering closer and closer to Gridanian settlements, threatening the smallfolk and their livestock.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[オチュー狩り]],},[609]={name_fr=[[Défi: Cassienova]],class_level_max=48,name_de=[[Ein Happen Für Cassie]],name=[[The Squirrel Trapper's Wife]],class_level=43,help_en=[[The grieving widow of a squirrel trapper has offered a bounty for the slaying of the beast that swallowed her husband whole─a sweet-breathed morbol called Capricious Cassie.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[気まぐれ婦人「カプリシャス・キャシー」]],},[610]={name_fr=[[Entre Deux Feux]],class_level_max=47,name_de=[[Schwere Entscheidung]],name=[[The Enemy Of My Enemy]],class_level=42,help_en=[[A band of tempered sylphs has engaged a party of imperial scouts most likely dispatched to the Twelveswood to spy on the Order of the Twin Adder. Wait for the sylphs to weaken the scouts and then finish off the Garlean invaders.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[ラークスコール遭遇戦]],},[611]={name_fr=[[Subjugués Ingrats]],class_level_max=47,name_de=[[Mehr Ist Nicht Genug]],name=[[The Enmity Of My Enemy]],class_level=42,help_en=[[An entry on gratitude missing from their dictionaries, the surviving sylphs have flown back to the Sylphlands to gather reinforcements...and launch an attack on you! Fend off the waves of budding beastmen while seeing that the lightly armed Mianne Thousandmalm stays in the realm of the living.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[続ラークスコール遭遇戦]],},[612]={name_fr=[[Défi: Une Option Sur L'optio]],class_level_max=49,name_de=[[Jetzt Oder Nie]],name=[[Below His Station]],class_level=44,help_en=[[Imperial pilus prior Aulus rem Vulso, accompanied by a thin retinue of soldiers, has embarked on a rare outing to personally observe warmachina wreckage. His defeat would deal the Empire a crushing blow. Do not let this chance slip away!]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[千人隊長「アウルス・レム・ヴルソ」]],},[615]={name_fr=[[Repénalisation]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Milchrausch]],name=[[Got Milkroot]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Milkroot is a curse upon the people of the Twelveswood, destroying lives and tearing apart families. The sylphs who grow the deadly drug must be dealt with, but until they can be found, we must concentrate our efforts on ridding the forest of the saplings.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[ミルク・クラッシュ]],},[616]={name_fr=[[Défi: Daxio Le Chimiste]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Gar Nicht So Harmlos]],name=[[Breaking Dawn]],class_level=47,help_en=[[Tempered sylphs have prepared a feast for Daxio of the Dawn─a powerful weaver of spells who uses milkroot to conjure visions of the future. The revelry must be stopped lest the sylphs defile the sacred forest and anger the elementals.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[幽谷の薬師「覚醒のダキシオ」]],},[618]={name_fr=[[Un Rêve Sans Fin]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Traumkröten Für Den Eigenbedarf]],name=[[Handful Of Dreams]],class_level=49,help_en=[[To induce even more powerful visions, tempered sylphs add the excretions of dreamtoads to their milkroot solutions. This blend, however, oft proves too toxic for the unknowing taker, and can lead to coma or even death. Little can be done to stop the production of milkroot, but the fewer toads to gather oil from, the harder it will be for the sylphs to brew the more potent varieties.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[ビューティフル・ドリーマー]],},[619]={name_fr=[[Défi: Vilain Volxia]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Sylphenkommandantin]],name=[[Bush Blade]],class_level=47,help_en=[[Elder sylph Volxia of the Blade has begun his daily rounds of the Sylphlands. Use this opportunity to slay the leader and weaken the beast tribe from the top down.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[幽谷の衛士「葉刃のヴォルキシア」]],},[620]={name_fr=[[Flapi Chapeau]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Ende Der Pilzsaison]],name=[[Everything's Better]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Masters of poisons, the sylphs utilize all manner of the forest's flora and fauna to create their deadly tinctures. One of those materials is a funguar known as the sylph bonnet for the hood-like shape of the cap. The poison from one cap can sicken an entire army, so it is best that the creatures are disposed of before the beastmen find them.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[とてとて楽しいキノコ狩り]],},[622]={name_fr=[[Défi: Une Pulsion Contre Pulxio]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Ramuh-Früherziehung]],name=[[The Gale That Rocks The Cradle]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Pulxio of the Short Gale is the stone-hearted sylph tasked with taking newly sprouted sylph bulbs away from the Seedbed for tempering. The first step in stopping a new generation of brainwashed sylphs from ruling the forest is to take Pulxio's life.]],map={placename={name=[[East Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[敬虔なる養育者「風狂のプルシオ」]],},[624]={name_fr=[[Vaincre Le Mal Par Les Racines]],class_level_max=38,name_de=[[Nicht Versumpfen]],name=[[Rogue On The Water]],class_level=33,help_en=[[Once a vast lake, home to myriad wavekin, the water of Rootslake has been sucked nigh dry by rogue sprites. Cull the creatures and restore the area's aetherial balance.]],map={placename={name=[[South Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[液状化現象]],},[626]={name_fr=[[Tortues Torturées]],class_level_max=35,name_de=[[Abgelenkt]],name=[[To Train A Tortoise]],class_level=30,help_en=[[The ragtag band of cutthroats and thieves known collectively as the Redbelly Wasps have got it in their heads that an adamantoise might be trained to crush their enemies, and now they dart about Rootslake poking and prodding the otherwise peaceful giants into a frenzy. Cuff the troublemakers before the entire area is overrun with angry adamantoises.]],map={placename={name=[[South Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[カメェェェッー！]],},[627]={name_fr=[[Traitement Des Eaux Usées]],class_level_max=36,name_de=[[Stinkt Zum Himmel]],name=[[Fate Is A Fecal Mistress]],class_level=31,help_en=[[The countless steaming pools of fecal ooze left by the stropers who have invaded Rootslake since its waters were drained are making those stationed at the nearby camp sick and unfit to fight. Help is sought in clearing the area of the vined creatures in a last-ditch effort to clear the air.]],map={placename={name=[[South Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[臭い物にはフタをしろ]],},[628]={name_fr=[[Défi: Phaïa Pas L'inviter]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Grimmiges Beißendes]],name=[[What Gored Before]],class_level=46,help_en=[[Trained for boar fighting by a sylph elder, Phaia had not fought two battles before turning on his master and consuming him in a single bite. Now the former champion of the boar pits roams free in the wood, goring those foolish enough to stand in his way.]],map={placename={name=[[South Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[最後の闘猪王「パイア」]],},[631]={name_fr=[[Touche Pas à Mon Arbre !]],class_level_max=42,name_de=[[Versuchter Frevel]],name=[[Don't Disturb This Grove]],class_level=37,help_en=[[Gods' Quiver outrunners have spotted several Ixal felling trees within the sacred boundary of the Hedge. Adventurers nearby are asked to drive the beastmen back north out of the Twelveswood.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[伐採部隊迎撃戦]],},[632]={name_fr=[[Défi: Les Morts En Marche]],class_level_max=51,name_de=[[Skandal Im Sperrgebiet]],name=[[Rude Awakening]],class_level=48,help_en=[[Damage wrought by the Calamity has freed frightening apparitions long bound to the forest for terrible deeds committed in ages past. A vengeful spirit given the name Daedalus is one such prisoner. Send the silent knight back to his eternal prison beneath the loam.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[遺跡の亡霊騎士「ダイダロス」]],},[633]={name_fr=[[Raid Sur Le Site De Déboisement Ixal]],class_level_max=50,name_de=[[Illegaler Holzexport]],name=[[Air Supply]],class_level=47,help_en=[[The Gods' Quiver seeks volunteers to join a raid of the Ixali logging grounds, the main targets being not the Ixal themselves, but the airstones the swiftbeaks use to give their war balloons flight.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[イクサル軍伐採所強襲作戦]],},[634]={name_fr=[[Défi: Chêne Déchaîné]],class_level_max=42,name_de=[[Wie Man In Den Wald Ruft]],name=[[Smells Like Tree Spirit]],class_level=37,help_en=[[Angered at the needless felling of his brethren, the Great Oak has lifted his roots from the Twelveswood floor and has set out to exact revenge...on anything without roots.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[怒れる守護者「グレートオーク」]],},[637]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Baron Rouge]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Spritfresser]],name=[[The Red Baron]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Fat on the ceruleum of the surrounding fields, the bomb baron has grown bold and now makes his way to the Ceruleum Processing Plant, intent on draining its tanks and then self-destructing in one brilliant blaze of glory, taking half of northern Thanalan with him. Stop the hot-headed voidsent before his plan can be brought to fruition.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[灼熱の男爵「ボムバロン」]],},[638]={name_fr=[[Précieux Céruleum]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Nur Quarz Im Schädel]],name=[[Just A Sip]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Quartz doblyns have gathered near the Ceruleum Processing Plant in search of food, that food being none other than ceruleum. Amajina & Sons will not stand idly by and watch as their profits are sucked down by pesky soulkin, and entreat adventurers to deal with the problem immediately.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[ゴクゴクドブラン]],},[639]={name_fr=[[Chacun Sa Tour]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Augen Auf]],name=[[East Meets Worst]],class_level=49,help_en=[[For no apparent reason, a flock of voidsent ahrimans has chosen to harass the keepers of the east watchtower. Entrusted with more important tasks, such as watching, the soldiers have issued a plea to all nearby adventurers to gather and drive away the creatures─preferably to somewhere in the vicinity of the west watchtower.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[監視者の影]],},[641]={name_fr=[[Piège De Quartz]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Durstige Dobalosse]],name=[[Twinkle, Twinkle Little Trap]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Ever the pests, a gaggle of quartz doblyns has dug into a patch of land near the Royal Allagan Starway, where they wait for caravans carrying ceruleum back to Ul'dah for sale and export. Many of the caravans do not have the means of clearing the roads themselves and request the aid of able-bodied adventurers.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[鋼虫の罠]],},[642]={name_fr=[[La Route Du Céruleum]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Ehrenwache]],name=[[The Ceruleum Road]],class_level=49,help_en=[[A frugal merchant bound for the Ceruleum Processing Plant to discuss business was abandoned by the two bodyguards he hired in Ul'dah after refusing to give in to their demands for more coin. Now, but a few malms from the plant, he finds himself helpless, and seeks to employ an adventurer to accompany him for the remainder of his journey.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[セルリウムロード]],},[643]={name_fr=[[Culte Maudit: L'enlèvement]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Von Kultisten Entführt]],name=[[Dark Devices - The Plea]],class_level=49,help_en=[[A poor farmer named Addison claims his only daughter was captured and taken away by the Lambs of Dalamud─a frightening cult which, even after the fall of the lesser moon, still offers blood sacrifices to their false god in hopes of currying his favor. The farmer seeks aid in reclaiming that which was ripped from his hands.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[救世神の生贄：誘拐編]],},[644]={name_fr=[[Culte Maudit: L'embuscade]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Unkluge Kultisten]],name=[[Dark Devices - The Bait]],class_level=49,help_en=[[It seems the tale told by Addison was a trap to lure you into the Lambs of Dalamud's grasp. Slay the cultists or become their next sacrifice!]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[救世神の生贄：待伏編]],},[645]={name_fr=[[Culte Maudit: L'aveu]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Die Sektenführer]],name=[[Dark Devices - The Switch]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Not to see their diabolical plans thwarted by a non-believer, Twin-tongued Addison and his daughter Milburh the Malicious step forth from the shadows. Slay the family and send them plummeting to the seventh hell so that they might join their master.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[救世神の生贄：誅殺編]],},[646]={name_fr=[[Culte Maudit: L'affront]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Ergreifendes Opfer]],name=[[Dark Devices - The End]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Sensing defeat, Milburh the Malicious sacrifices her carnal form to the void where a succubus claims it for her own. Strike down the cultist and drive the voidsent from her corpse.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[救世神の生贄：妖異編]],},[647]={name_fr=[[Défi: Gorgimère Indigne]],class_level_max=52,name_de=[[Etwas Von Allem]],name=[[Go, Go, Gorgimera]],class_level=49,help_en=[[Created by a madman employing forbidden alchemy and fell magicks, the gorgimera is a bastardization that cannot be allowed to roam free, lest it spread its taint across the entire realm.]],map={placename={name=[[Northern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[荒れ狂う巨獣「ゴーキマイラ」]],},[649]={name_fr=[[La Famille Avant Tout]],class_level_max=17,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Nicht Ohne Meine Eier]],name=[[Sister Crustacean]],class_level=12,help_en=[[A spawning megalocrab will do whatever it takes to see its brood safe, and that includes using its powerful claws to dismember Lalafellin fishers who draw too close to the wavekin's unhatched offspring. Slay a crab, save a lad.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[その水棲動物を見よ]],},[650]={name_fr=[[Défi: Volatile Carnivore]],class_level_max=17,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Der Kleine Nimmersatt]],name=[[Tender Buttons]],class_level=12,help_en=[[Gluttonous Gertrude was just another plump dodo on the farm...until she bit the arse off one of the stable boys at Swiftperch and escaped into Quarterstone. Seek out the ravenous bird and slay her before another rump goes missing.]],map={placename={name=[[Western La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[暴食の怪鳥「グルタナスガーティ」]],},[651]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Créature Inconnue]],class_level_max=31,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Bestie Aus Der Anderswelt]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Armored Beast]],class_level=26,help_en=[[The Brass Blades are hopelessly overmatched by an armored beast of unknown origin. Help Lightning defeat the hulking creature, and save the struggling soldiers from a bloody fate.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：巨獣迎撃戦]],},[652]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Créature Inconnue]],class_level_max=31,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Bestie Aus Der Anderswelt]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Armored Beast]],class_level=26,help_en=[[The Brass Blades are hopelessly overmatched by an armored beast of unknown origin. Help Lightning defeat the hulking creature, and save the struggling soldiers from a bloody fate.]],map={placename={name=[[Eastern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：巨獣迎撃戦]],},[653]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Cuirassé Outrecuidant]],class_level_max=43,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Killermaschine Aus Der Anderswelt]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Dread On Arrival]],class_level=38,help_en=[[A magitek-like machine is running rampant, threatening all nearby with its uncontrolled thrashing. Join Lightning in dismantling this dreadful contraption.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：機獣討伐戦]],},[654]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Cuirassé Outrecuidant]],class_level_max=43,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Killermaschine Aus Der Anderswelt]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Dread On Arrival]],class_level=38,help_en=[[A magitek-like machine is running rampant, threatening all nearby with its uncontrolled thrashing. Join Lightning in dismantling this dreadful contraption.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Central Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：機獣討伐戦]],},[655]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Anubis Annonciateurs]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Vorboten Des Chaos]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Anubys Assault]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The mindless tide of chaos threatens to flood the realm of Eorzea. Fight at Lightning's side as she seeks to repel the Anubys invaders that herald the coming of unthinkable doom.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：アヌビス殲滅戦]],},[656]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Anubis Annonciateurs]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Vorboten Des Chaos]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - Anubys Assault]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The mindless tide of chaos threatens to flood the realm of Eorzea. Fight at Lightning's side as she seeks to repel the Anubys invaders that herald the coming of unthinkable doom.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：アヌビス殲滅戦]],},[657]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Le Dragon Du Chaos]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Herr Des Chaos]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - On Wings Of Chaos]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The mindless tide of chaos threatens to flood the realm of Eorzea. Fight at Lightning's side as she faces a terrible incarnation of chaotic energy.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：屍竜討滅戦]],},[658]={name_fr=[[Retour D'éclair: Le Dragon Du Chaos]],class_level_max=50,patch={number=[[2.05]],},name_de=[[Herr Des Chaos]],name=[[Lightning Strikes - On Wings Of Chaos]],class_level=45,help_en=[[The mindless tide of chaos threatens to flood the realm of Eorzea. Fight at Lightning's side as she faces a terrible incarnation of chaotic energy.]],map={placename={name=[[Mor Dhona]],},},name_ja=[[閃光の影向：屍竜討滅戦]],},[660]={name_fr=[[Fort Comme Une Brique: Golems]],class_level_max=12,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Golems Aus Einer Anderen Welt]],name=[[Brick By Brick]],class_level=7,help_en=[[A cadre of earthen brickmen appears!
Watch your back, and defeat these lumbering golems!]],map={placename={name=[[Central Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[不思議な魔物「ゴーレム」]],},[661]={name_fr=[[Fort Comme Une Brique: Golem De Pierre]],class_level_max=12,patch={number=[[2.1]],},name_de=[[Der Steingolem Aus Einer Anderen Welt]],name=[[Brick By Stone Brick]],class_level=7,help_en=[[A stone brickman appears!
