nd flapping fins.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[キャッチ・アンド・リリース]],},[726]={name_fr=[[Noix Farceuses]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Dumme Nuss]],name=[[The Nuts]],class_level=54,help_en=[[In retrospect, stuffing an archaeosaur's nostrils full of kupo nuts while it slept probably wasn't the best of ideas. So sayeth the mischievous moogle currently fleeing for its life from a pack of bloodthirsty scalekin.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[さよならアルケオダイノス]],},[727]={name_fr=[[Défi: C'est Complètement Glycon]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Von Schwarzem Blut]],name=[[Glycon Air]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Direct descendant of the vengeful Tioman, Glycon's blood runs as black as that of his progenitor. Slay the dark dragon and grant his troubled soul peace.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[黒竜の使徒「グリコン」]],},[728]={name_fr=[[Pile Ou Face Mog]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Teures Hobby]],name=[[Coin Toss]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Some moogles are slaves to fashion, others to fortune. And then there are those who are slaves to both and create their fashion out of other's fortunes─in this case, a necklace made of old coins on a string. Coins collected by you, of course.]],name_ja=[[モーグリ金融道]],},[731]={name_fr=[[Mangeurs De Mogs]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Zum Fressen Gern]],name=[[Supper Time]],class_level=54,help_en=[[There is one thing that an archaeosaur enjoys more than feeding, and that is feeding on plump, juicy moogles. Stop the slavering scalekin before they make their way into Moghome.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[失われた世界]],},[732]={name_fr=[[Équilibre élémentaire]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vorsicht Hochspannung]],name=[[Sprite Club]],class_level=54,help_en=[[It has been observed that increased activity by lightning-aspected dragons is accompanied by an increase in sprites of the same charge. Slay the sprites and restore aetherial balance to the area.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[雲海に轟く雷鳴]],},[735]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mog En Un Seul Morceau]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Schlecht Gekaut Ist Halb Unverdaut]],name=[[Whole Food]],class_level=54,help_en=[[No, that frantic flurry of “kupos” you hear is not your imagination, but the sound of an unlucky moogle swallowed whole by Abelisk─a towering archaeosaur with an insatiable appetite. Help slice open a path to freedom before the big lizard's bile does its work.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[飽食の恐竜「アベリスク」]],},[736]={name_fr=[[Tulihänds à Tuer]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Alle Hände Voll Zu Tun]],name=[[Say It Tulihand]],class_level=54,help_en=[[The Dravanian Horde is gathering forces for an aerial attack on Ishgard proper. Scatter the tulihands as they arrive, putting an end to the assault before it begins.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[トゥリヘンド・スクランブル]],},[737]={name_fr=[[Vouivre Ou Mourir]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vivel La Revolution]],name=[[Vouivre Believre]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Infuriated at the foiling of their plot, the vouivres who called for the tulihand assault on Ishgard's walls have gathered to mete punishment on the meager mortals who would so foolishly stand against the Horde.]],name_ja=[[トゥリヘンド・ベロシティ]],},[738]={name_fr=[[Défi: Waugyl Le Belliqueux]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ich Bin Der Waugyl]],name=[[Waugyl Waugyl Waugyl]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Master of the Monsterie, Waugyl the Warring has descended from his perch to prey on those bold, or foolhardy, enough to make the winding journey through the Landlord Colony.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[遺跡の番人「ウォーギル」]],},[740]={name_fr=[[Danse Avec Les Dragons]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Tanz Mit Den Drachen]],name=[[How To Cane Your Dragon]],class_level=54,help_en=[[A small band of lesser dragons serving the mighty Nidhogg has begun assailing Zenith in a rather futile attempt to topple the spire and please their ever-wroth master. Show the dragons the glimmer of your steel and drive them off before any grave damage is done.]],name_ja=[[竜との舞踏]],},[741]={name_fr=[[Nouvelle Danse Avec Les Dragons]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Tanz Mit Den Wolken]],name=[[Aevis Has Left The Building]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Enraged at seeing their brethren sent back to their lairs with their tails 'twixt their legs, a pack of slightly less witless, yet far more arrogant cloud aevis have come to seek vengeance for pride wounded.]],name_ja=[[続・竜との舞踏]],},[742]={name_fr=[[Défi: Asah Commence à Bien Faire]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Hindernis Auf Der Fahrbahn]],name=[[Asah, I Came, I Conquered]],class_level=54,help_en=[[The road to Asah is already perilous enough without an adamantine monstrosity blocking passage and sucking the marrow from the bones of unfortunate travelers. Slay Cuelebre and ensure that if travelers are to have their marrow sucked, it will not be because of a road-blocking dragon.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[甲鱗の猛竜「クエレブレ」]],},[744]={name_fr=[[Défi: Marre De Fjalar]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Fjalar Gegen Den Rest Der Welt]],name=[[Waiting For Fjalar To Stall]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Mistdragon Fjalar, loyal subject to Hraesvelgr, maintains his vigilant watch over Zenith and the Churning Mists as he awaits the return of his lord. There are those, however, who would see Fjalar fail at his task─minions of the hate-driven Nidhogg.]],name_ja=[[夜と霧]],},[746]={name_fr=[[Wyverne De Représailles]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Brennt, Wyvern, Brennt!]],name=[[Don't Know Wyvern]],class_level=56,help_en=[[Elder wyverns serving the Dravanian Horde have returned to the Churning Mists after completing a deadly assault on Ishgardian settlements in Coerthas. Attack the creatures while their wounds are still fresh, and see that they never return to the lower realm.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[燃えよワイバーン]],},[747]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Vengeance Du Vigile]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Tag Der Abrechnung]],name=[[From Dusk Till Gone]],class_level=55,help_en=[[One of the final, and most infamous Horde assaults on the Dusk Vigil before the stronghold's eventual fall was the massacre helmed by the merciless wyvern Minaruja. Since that day, the knights of Ishgard have sworn vengeance. Mayhap this is the day it shall be had.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[薄暮の飛竜「ミナルジャ」]],},[748]={name_fr=[[De Quoi Je Me Mélias?]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Meliaden-Marmelade]],name=[[Treehouse Of The Spirits]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Blood spilled in recent battles has soaked the dry soil of the Churning Mists, drawing forth thirstful spirits such as the arboreal meliae. As always, satisfaction will not be found in the amount retrieved, and they will soon turn to attacking the living to wet their tongues.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[来たのは誰だ]],},[751]={name_fr=[[Défi: Kucedre Le Maudit]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Der Angeschwärzte]],name=[[As The World Burns]],class_level=56,help_en=[[As if slaughtering defenseless Ishgardians was not enough, the high dragon Kucedre will go out of his way to defile the most sacred of Ishgardian monuments, so that we may ever be reminded of his power. Slay the unforgivable villain and bring peace to the land once again.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[猛炎の焔竜「クシェドレ」]],},[752]={name_fr=[[Des Mogs Au Ménage]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Putzkolonnen-Eskorte]],name=[[It's The Moogle, Reinvented]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Bound by ancient covenant entered with Hraesvelgr, the moogles of the Churning Mists will periodically make the journey to Zenith to clean the sacred spire of any defilement done at the hands of Nidhogg's underlings. A recent increase in Horde activity, however, has made the journey impossible without escort.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[吸引力は変わらない]],},[753]={name_fr=[[Défi: Châtiment Kupporel]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Großes Kupowetter]],name=[[Corporal Pomishment]],class_level=54,help_en=[[A thorough scolding by Mogpo the Magnificent was not enough to convince Mogoosh the Misbehaving that his recent run of mischief has put the lives of all Moghome's moogles in peril. Mogpo has asked you to rough up the rascal until he repents.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[雲海の問題児「悪童のモグーシ」]],},[754]={name_fr=[[Galar En Galère]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Sonne Gegen Schatten]],name=[[Infamous]],class_level=55,help_en=[[The Horde has temporarily turned its vengeful gaze from Ishgard to the few dragons who still maintain their allegiance to Hraesvelgr─Galar of the Second Sun being one such acolyte. Aid the aged dragon in driving back his assailants before he succumbs to the wounds already dealt him.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[聖と邪の交わるひずみ]],},[755]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mogvais Garçon]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Immer Auf Die Kleinen]],name=[[Ain't Misbehaving]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Mogoosh is back to his misbehaving ways, this time picking on someone his own size, a brood of newborn dragonlings nesting in Zenith. The good moogles of Moghome have tried reasoning with the mischief-maker, but now seek a more...painful form of persuasion.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[愚行の問題児「悪童のモグーシ」]],},[756]={name_fr=[[Bouts De Ferraille]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Krawallmetaller]],name=[[Metal Gears Rising]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Rumors of a new “whizzlepop” gear being developed by the diabolical Illuminati have Idyllshire inhabitants worried for their well-being. All they need do now is acquire several whizzlepops from Illuminati members to find out exactly what the contraptions are and if there actually is any cause for concern.]],name_ja=[[悪魔の機械]],},[757]={name_fr=[[Vengeurs De Ferraille]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Rache Der Schwermetaller]],name=[[Metal Gears Revengeance]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Seeking retribution for whizzlepops fizzled, a party of Illuminati revengers has been dispatched into the Arkhitekton. Slay the gate-crashing goblins and put an end to their virulent vendetta.]],name_ja=[[リベンジャーズ]],},[758]={name_fr=[[Défi: Vengeurs De Ferraille II]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vollmetallalchemisten]],name=[[Metal Gears Revengeance 2]],class_level=58,help_en=[[The old adage that revenge is a dish best served cold unfortunately does not translate well into gobbiespeak, and the Illuminati have deployed a massive magitek vangob, seeking further revenge for the quashing of their first (failed) attempt at revenge.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[全面改修機「III号ゴブリガードJ型」]],},[759]={name_fr=[[Tarentules En Rupture De Stock]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Nicht Spinne, Nicht Falke]],name=[[Tarantula Hawk, Pro Stinger]],class_level=58,help_en=[[A lack of tarantulas in the Dravanian hinterlands has tarantula hawks seeking other potential victims to serve as nourishment for their larvae. Exterminate the swarm before they set their compound eyes on puppies or kittens or baby Lalafells.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[タランチュラホークの襲撃]],},[760]={name_fr=[[D'une Pierre Deux Nuisibles]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Doppelte Schädlingsbekämpfung]],name=[[Wild Wilde Death]],class_level=58,help_en=[[What does one do when two breeds of pests known for destroying crops and raiding pens are found fighting each other for territorial dominance? Why, use the opportunity to slay both, what else?]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[ワイルドでいこう！]],},[761]={name_fr=[[Défi: Une épitaphe Pour Épaphos]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Ging Ins Auge]],name=[[Gets The Red Out]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Thought to have been bred by a Sharlayan alchemist who was working on an improved recipe for eye drops, Epaphus was abandoned by his master during the exodus which emptied the northwestern city-state, leaving the beast to wreak havoc on the lives of those few who remained.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[巨眼の魔牛「エパポス」]],},[762]={name_fr=[[Le Bal Des Demoiselles]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Kammerjägerkommando]],name=[[Makes The Very Best...Nests]],class_level=59,help_en=[[The absence of bibliothecaries in the Great Gubal Library since the Sharlayan's mass exodus back to their homeland has allowed all manner of vilekin─including the damselfly─to use the remaining tomes as nests. Exterminate the pests so that further damage to the library might be lessened.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[図書館清掃]],},[763]={name_fr=[[Rhume Des Narbroois]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Und Täglich Tropft Der Nasenschleim]],name=[[Olympus Has Pollen]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Despite their heavy-duty masks, the good goblins of Idyllshire have recently been plagued with watery eyes and sniffly snouts─the culprit believed to be the pollen of the narbroois. Until the beastmen can retool their masks to filter this irksome irritant, a bounty has been placed on the seedkin's heads.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[花粉前線異常アリ]],},[764]={name_fr=[[Défi: Ruginis à éliminer]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Sie Kam Aus Der Luft]],name=[[Feed Me, See More]],class_level=58,help_en=[[While most of Eorzea's carnivorous plants are immobile, limiting the danger they pose to other creatures, narbroois are not bound to the soil, making them possible threats to the realm's inhabitants─Ruginis being the biggest...and hungriest threat of all.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[吸血の浮遊草「ルギニス」]],},[766]={name_fr=[[Mécanismes à Enrayer]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Blaue Hände, Blaue Augen]],name=[[Pop Goes The Whizzle]],class_level=58,help_en=[[After failing to revenge the failed attempt at revenging the theft of their whizzlepops, the Illuminati have given up on revenge and simply decided that if they can't have the items, no one can, sending a small army to destroy them. Help the goblins of Idyllshire protect the whizzlepops, if only to simply spite the Illuminati.]],name_ja=[[ゴブゴブ紛争]],},[767]={name_fr=[[Défi: Moundrinix Le Virtuose]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Satz Mit X: Hubbelknix]],name=[[Revenge Of The Vengeful Revengeance]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Unable to exact revenge, exact revenge for an inability to exact revenge, or destroy crates because of an inability to exact revenge for an inability to exact revenge, the Illuminati have dispatched the highly decorated Moundrinx Eightclinks in a last-ditch effort to prove they are not nearly as incompetent as everyone now thinks.]],name_ja=[[熟練の戦闘指揮官「八丁のマウンドリンクス」]],},[768]={name_fr=[[Ratels Au Casse-pipe]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Von Wegen Tolle Wut]],name=[[Ratel And Hum]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Drawn to the waste piles of Bigwest Shortstop, a pack of diseased ratels has descended from the surrounding mountains to feed. As even a single bite will bring on a dread fever, it is crucial that the beasts be put down swiftly and without mercy.]],name_ja=[[尻尾を立てろ！]],},[769]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dobharch La Matriarche]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Zorn Einer Mutter]],name=[[Dobharch Did It For The Best]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Drawn to the dying screams of her children, Dobharch─ratel matron─has come seeking payment in blood for the lives lost in the previous day's culling.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[野獣の家長「ダルウフー」]],},[770]={name_fr=[[Écrabouillage D'Écrabouilleuse]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Keine Vesper Für Die Esper]],name=[[Infant Vangob]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Trouble with the jangletype vangob (namely that its jangling would give away its position to the enemy) has prompted the Illuminati to develop a new model of vangob─the espertype, supposedly capable of anticipating the movements of its targets. Destroy the prototypes before the goblins can begin mass production.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[西方電撃戦]],},[771]={name_fr=[[Morbol D'air Frais]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Große Stinken]],name=[[Morbol Man]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Seedlings forgotten in Saint Mocianne's Arboretum have since grown into ferocious great morbols. If that was not enough, southerlies off Mount Gubal carry the stench from their maws directly into Idyllshire where the unmasked residents are doomed to suffer until the winds change...or kind adventurers lend a helping hand.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[モルボルをブッコろせ]],},[772]={name_fr=[[Défi: Broyer Du Moira]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Melancholie Und Die Unendliche Unersättlichkeit]],name=[[On Melancholic Hill]],class_level=58,help_en=[[What tragic event brought unbalance to poor Moira's humours, resulting in an excess of black bile is unknown. What is known is that the overgrown morbol has already devoured three goblins, four Lalafells, and a rolanberry cake baked to celebrate the nameday of Idyllshire's oldest resident. The seedkin must be stopped before any more pastry is lost.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[憂鬱なる令嬢「メランコリック・モイラ」]],},[773]={name_fr=[[Bruan Aime, Bruan Reste]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Platz An Der Sonnenbärspeisetafel]],name=[[Sun Bear, Sun Bear, What Do You Eat]],class_level=58,help_en=[[It is said that once a sun bear acquires a taste for the flesh of man, it will eat nothing else. Two missing Miqo'te lovers who were last seen in the Answering Quarter─an area now overrun with violent sun bears─suggest that taste has already been acquired.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[イディルシャイア猟友会]],},[774]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dubhe Ration]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Krieger, Grüß Mir Die Sonne]],name=[[The Bear Up There]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Dravanian folklore tells of a mighty Hellsguard forty hands tall who wrestled with Dubhe─the deadliest sun bear on all Abalathia's Spine. Nothing more is mentioned of the Roegadyn, but Dubhe still terrorizes the land today.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[血濡れの暴君「ドゥーベ」]],},[775]={name_fr=[[Pauvres Bruans]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vögel Gegen Bären]],name=[[The Birds And The Bears]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Sun bears will often raid the nests of cockatrices looking for eggs to crack open and devour. This practice, obviously, is not looked kindly upon by mother cockatrices who will furiously defend their broods to the death. Bears weakened from cockatrice attacks, however, make easy prey for adventurers looking to earn a little extra coin.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[悲しみのベアー]],},[777]={name_fr=[[Escorte De Poroggo]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Molchaugen, Unkenzehen]],name=[[Poroggo Stuck]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Sent on an errand by her master to fetch eye of newt and toe of frog, Maro Roggo finds herself unable to return with the items, for the road home is now bristling with blood-lusting beasts. Escort the poor poroggo safely back to her master and receive a hefty reward.]],name_ja=[[使い魔はつらいよ]],},[778]={name_fr=[[Des Poroggos Courroucés]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Jetzt Schlägt's Drei Zehen]],name=[[Frog Days Of Summer]],class_level=59,help_en=[[When abandoning their Eorzean settlement, the Sharlayans left more than their tomes and their tuffets, they left their poroggo familiars, who now, after waiting patiently for their masters to return home, have decided it is time to release nigh on twenty summers of pent-up rage.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[蛙のために弔鐘は鳴る]],},[779]={name_fr=[[Vilains Opkens]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wasserschutzpolizei]],name=[[Toss 'Em Back]],class_level=58,help_en=[[A school of migrating opken have infested the waters of the Dravanian hinterlands, eating anything and everything the wavekin can fit their maws about, including fish harvested by the goblins of Idyllshire. Seek out the scaled abominations and send them back to the sea.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[シャーレアンの影]],},[780]={name_fr=[[Le Bien Dérobé D'un Bibliophile Voleur]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Bücher Sind Für Fische Nichts]],name=[[Tome Raider]],class_level=58,help_en=[[On his way back home from the Great Gubal Library, a school of opken attacked young Browfix Turnalot, ripping from his grasp the ancient folios he had collected from the abandoned house of tomes. Browfix seeks assistance in retrieving what he rightfully stole.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[ビブロフィリアの憂鬱]],},[781]={name_fr=[[Cocatrix De Bibliothèque]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Bücherhühner]],name=[[Cockatrice Block]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Several domesticated cockatrices have escaped from their coop and taken up residence in the Great Gubal Library, tearing apart priceless tomes to create makeshift nests atop guano-striped bookshelves. The cloudkin will, however, emerge to hunt, offering a rare opportunity for capture.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[コカトリスの思い出]],},[782]={name_fr=[[Biféricéras à Terrasser]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Bifericeras Müssen Weg]],name=[[Come Shells Or High Water]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Without any natural predators in the Dravanian hinterlands, the population of bifericeras introduced to the area by goblins for harvesting has increased exponentially. The residents of Idyllshire are seeking brave men and women to cull their numbers.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[果しなき流れの果てで]],},[783]={name_fr=[[Défi: Triste Bero Roggo]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Einsamkeit Des Poroggo-Familiars]],name=[[Toad Alone]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Poor Bero Roggo is just one of many poroggo familiars abandoned by their masters when the Sharlayan exodus took place. Bero, however, never forgot the pain of waking up alone, and has since sworn revenge on anyone who even reminds him of his former life.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[主を待つ者「孤独のベロ・ロッゴ」]],},[784]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Poisson Bipède Et Vorace]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Er Kam Von Weitem übers Meer]],name=[[How Do You Feed A Hungry Manlike Monster]],class_level=59,help_en=[[A remarkably ravenous breed of opken, the oplo opken will devour upwards of a hundred fish a day to fill their seemingly bottomless bellies, moving on once an area has been gutted. Though they appear manlike, the opken are more monster than man─the end of a blade the only reason they will heed.]],name_ja=[[魚喰いの魚人「オプロケプロン」]],},[785]={name_fr=[[Prendre Les Gens Pour Des Cocons]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Kriech Mir Aus Den Augen]],name=[[Out Of The Woodwork]],class_level=58,help_en=[[Crawlers have infested Saint Mocianne's Arboretum and are transforming the entire building into a giant cocoon from which more crawlers will eventually emerge. Squash the vilekin...and don't forget to wipe your buskins on the grass.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[クロウラーの巣]],},[786]={name_fr=[[Défi: Défiler Habetrot]],class_level_max=62,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Ganz Großer Spinner]],name=[[Silkworm]],class_level=58,help_en=[[The cyclopean crawler Habetrot is a weaver most wicked, and will spin his silk about anything that moves, including his own kin. It is high time the vilekin's threads were snapped.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Hinterlands]],},},name_ja=[[糸紡ぎ巧者「ハベロット」]],},[787]={name_fr=[[Observateurs Surveillés]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Was Gibt's Da Zu Glotzen?]],name=[[Eye In The Sky]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Many of the knights stationed in the Coerthas western highlands to watch the skies for Horde activity complain of a constant feeling of being watched themselves...by giant furry eyes nonetheless. Search the area for the peeping prowlers and provide them with a slightly more permanent form of “shut-eye.”]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[誰か見てるぞ！]],},[788]={name_fr=[[Une Histoire De Crottin]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ins Bocknäpfchen Getreten]],name=[[A Dung Deal]],class_level=50,help_en=[[A noblewoman who recently visited the Pike and Anvil lodged a formal complaint with the Falcon's Nest garrison commander, threatening to strip him of his land and titles after stepping in a rather ripe pile of dung left by the steinbocks which graze in the area. The message is clear─either the beasts go, or he goes.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[巡礼の騎士]],},[789]={name_fr=[[Savoir Briser La Glace]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wasser Ist Zum Waschen Da]],name=[[Land Of The Freeze]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Ice sprites blown off the windswept Gorgagne Holding and into Camp Riversmeet are freezing all the outpost's drinking water. Slay the spirits and ensure thirsts stay slaked.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[凍結スリップ注意！]],},[791]={name_fr=[[Dans Le Mylodon]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Revierausweitung]],name=[[Dawn Of The Mylodons]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Upland mylodons have lumbered their way atop the Black Iron Bridge to bathe in the short winter sun, and refuse to budge, impeding the progress of supply wains going to and from Falcon's Nest. Drive the beasts back so that the deliveries might recommence.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[黒鉄橋の戦い]],},[792]={name_fr=[[Défi: Les Veules Et La Velue]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Peluda Tobt]],name=[[Don Of The Mylodons]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Displeased by their violent displacement from the sunbaked stones of the Black Iron Bridge, the upland mylodons have lumbered back, this time accompanied by their great elder, Peluda.]],name_ja=[[剛毛の白獣「ペルダ」]],},[793]={name_fr=[[Défi: Ne Pas Douter Face à Dzu Teh]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Rückkehr Des Yeti-Ritters]],name=[[We Fought A Dzu]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Numerous are the legends that tell of Dzu-Teh─a yeti as tall as the Craving Tree and as fast as the Swiftrun River. With a temper as hot as the waters of Dragonspit and a heart as cold as rime-locked Ashpool. With hair as white as the flour once ground at Gorgagne Mills and... In other words, he must needs be slain.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[ヤク喰い巨人「ズウティ」]],},[794]={name_fr=[[Crier Au Convictoire Trop Vite]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wem Ehre Gebührt]],name=[[True Convictions]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Ever yammering about how they seek the glory one might obtain by slaying a dragon, the moment a few archaeornis descend on their camp, the Convictors turn pleading eyes to nearby adventurers, seeking assistance in escaping the day with their lives...and to a lesser extent, their dignities.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[栄光の聖フィネア連隊]],},[795]={name_fr=[[Glacial Garde-manger]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ich Möchte Kein Eisbär Sein]],name=[[The Polar Express]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Food is scarce in the snow-covered north, so when Ishgardian knights bring in large quantities of rations to outfit their camps, it is only a matter of time before all manner of hungry creatures descend from the mountains looking for a bite. Drive away the beasts to keep the knights' bellies full.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[熊出没注意]],},[796]={name_fr=[[Défi: Gare Aux Piège-yétis]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Den Mund Zu Voll Genommen]],name=[[Apparent Trap]],class_level=50,help_en=[[While the name “yetitrap” implies that the seedkin is physically capable of actually trapping a full-grown yeti, it is highly unlikely that even a Lalafell's forearm would fit in the plant's mouth. That does not mean, however, that they should be left to roam free nipping at Lalafellin limbs.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[雪男の天敵「イエティトラップ」]],},[798]={name_fr=[[Plus Moche Que Méchant]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wärmflasche Wider Willen]],name=[[Abominable Me]],class_level=51,help_en=[[On especially cold nights, yetis from the Slate Mountains will journey down to Dragonspit to find warmth in the thermal pools. On their way back, they will oft raid nearby farms, stealing livestock and the occasional child, whom they keep alive until back in their dens so they may drink the blood hot.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[獣人雪男]],},[800]={name_fr=[[Requiem Pour Un Dragon]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Traum Ist Aus]],name=[[Requiem For A Dragon]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Ever since its exposure following the Calamity, the ice encasing the Dreaming Dragon of Ashpool has been slowly melting, releasing into the nearby air the fetid stench of rotting dragon flesh─a stench that is now driving local fauna into a frenzy. Slay the slavering wooly yaks and polar bears drawn to the dragon before they set their sights on you.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[臥竜島の戦い]],},[801]={name_fr=[[Extermination De Piège-grésils]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Man Jätet, Was Man Sieht]],name=[[Follow The Sleet]],class_level=50,help_en=[[The endless winter brought by the Calamity has rendered the once lush Gorgagne Holding a frozen wasteland where naught but man-eating sleet traps thrive. But, as the saying goes, an empty wasteland is better than one teeming with deadly seedkin, so take up your swords and slice away.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[凍った花]],},[802]={name_fr=[[Qui A Peur De La Meute Géante?]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Stärke Des Rudels]],name=[[Sick Pack]],class_level=51,help_en=[[When the climate in the highlands changed, once fiercely independent wolf packs began doing the unthinkable─combining, forming super packs so as to increase chances of survival in their new harsh environment. These super packs now pose a serious threat to the knights stationed in the area, and assistance is sought in controlling their numbers.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[ダスクの銀狼]],},[805]={name_fr=[[Congédier Les Commandants Gelés]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Geringere Übel]],name=[[In Command]],class_level=51,help_en=[[If anything is worse than being maimed by an ice commander, it is being buried alive in an avalanche caused by an ice commander and wishing in the final moments before suffocation that you had instead been maimed by an ice commander. Rid the area of ice commanders, and alleviate the need to worry about either.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[コマンダー！]],},[807]={name_fr=[[Défi: Taper Dans L'œil]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Im Auge Des Betrachters]],name=[[What You See Is What You Get]],class_level=50,help_en=[[It is said that when gazing into the eye of the Beholder, a man can see his deepest desires─those desires usually involving escape from the iron grip of the Beholder's wicked claws.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[幻惑の視線「ビホルダー」]],},[809]={name_fr=[[Entre Appétit Et Dégoût]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Unliebsame Nichtsgesandtschaft]],name=[[Panic Rheum]],class_level=50,help_en=[[A voidsent by any other name would still be as unsweet as the deceptively sweet-sounding gelato. Case in point, the rheum (though its name is not very sweet-sounding to begin with). In addition to not being very sweet, both are also very deadly, and if the first is not reason enough to cull their numbers, the second definitely is.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[スノーホワイト]],},[810]={name_fr=[[Défi: Tartufo Et Truffe Blanche]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Hungerspiele]],name=[[Sugar, Sugar]],class_level=50,help_en=[[One can tell how well fed an area's residents are by listening to the names given to everyday creatures─playful monikers such as Tartufo and White Truffle suggesting that starvation-induced delirium is causing everything to resemble food. Unable to fight on empty stomachs, the people of Coerthas seek a better-nourished hero to save them.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[人喰い氷菓「タルトゥフォ＆ホワイトトリュフ」]],},[811]={name_fr=[[La Chasse Aux Archéornis]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Kampf Gegen Die Vorhut]],name=[[Unsilent Vigil]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Several archaeornis have flown over Lancegate and begun gathering near the Dusk Vigil. Fearing an attack by the Dravanian Horde near, the knights in the area have put a call out to adventurers requesting assistance in dispersing the flock.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[竜の眷属を討て]],},[812]={name_fr=[[Défi: Arrête De Picolaton]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Kampf Gegen Die Hauptstreitmacht]],name=[[Pico De Gallows]],class_level=51,help_en=[[While swift adventurer action has left the archaeornis flock in a state of disarray, the effort may have come too late, as scouts now report the arrival of Picolaton─a terrifying creature known to lay waste to entire companies of knights without suffering more than a few ruffled feathers.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[鳥竜の大王「ピコラトン」]],},[813]={name_fr=[[Les Grands Méchants Loups Argentés]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wettlauf Mit Dem Tod]],name=[[Run, Riders, Run]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Outriders belonging to House Durendaire have been spotted fleeing from a pack of silver wolves which, despite losing over half of its number to the knights' steel, remains in pursuit, knowing the knights cannot run forever. Hurry to the outriders' aid before their legs fail them.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[氷上の狼]],},[814]={name_fr=[[Défi: Heidrun L'insatiable]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Auf Den Geschmack Gekommen]],name=[[One Whiskey, One Goat, One Spear]],class_level=50,help_en=[[After stumbling upon a barrel of whiskey stored outside one of the Convictors' tents, Heidrun became one of the happiest mountain goats in Coerthas. Once the whiskey had disappeared, however, he transformed into one of the angriest, destroying large stocks of supplies in a futile search for another sip.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[酒浸り野獣「ヘイズルーン」]],},[815]={name_fr=[[Défi: Alaimbert Le Risible]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Herzallerwertest]],name=[[No Ifs, Ands, Or Butts]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Newly knighted Alaimbert of the Spiked Butt cannot understand why people are always laughing behind his back, so to prove he is worthy of their respect, he seeks a battle-hardened opponent with whom he may cross steel.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[若き竜騎士「鋭槍のアランベール」]],},[816]={name_fr=[[Adieu Aux Bergthurs]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Nach Hause Teleportieren]],name=[[Null And Void]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Summoned eons ago and then forgotten, bergthurs are voidsent trapped in a realm not their own, determined to tear their way back to the void even if it means destroying this world in the process.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[ファルコンネストの脅威]],},[817]={name_fr=[[Défi: Avec ça, On Est Werner]],class_level_max=55,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Heuchlerische Helden]],name=[[Dishonored]],class_level=51,help_en=[[Ser Werner and Ser Beaudonet of the Convictors have come to an impasse regarding who dealt the killing blow to a dragon (pup) that wandered into their camp (with a broken leg). Unwilling to even agree to disagree, Ser Werner has dishonored the Convictors and must be punished.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[功績泥棒「卑怯者のウェルナー」]],},[818]={name_fr=[[Défi: Un Mâle De Chocobo]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Erfüllung Eines Traums]],name=[[By The Horns]],class_level=52,help_en=[[From the day he is born, a chocobo hunter dreams of capturing an elusive bull chocobo. Fortunately, bull chocobos are abundant enough to provide all with the opportunity to fulfill this dream...whether it be yours or not.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[伝説の馬鳥「ブルチョコボ」]],},[819]={name_fr=[[De Mauvais Chasseurs, Ce Sont...]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Retter Des Chocobo-Waldes]],name=[[Ladies First]],class_level=52,help_en=[[A band of chocobo hunters banished from Tailfeather for trapping only female chocobos has been spotted near the Chocobo Forest doing what they do best. See that their next banishment is from the realm of the living.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[チョコボの森の番人]],},[820]={name_fr=[[Défi: Yowie Ne Vit Qu'une Fois]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Kopf Zu Groß]],name=[[Run, Run Away]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Swift legs and sharp beaks all but ensure that chocobos can survive the dangers of the Dravanian forelands. Some creatures, however, are simply too much for the majestic cloudkin, Yowie being one such terror.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[巧妙なる狩人「ヨーウィ」]],},[821]={name_fr=[[Ça En Vaut La Penne]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Mit Federn Macht Man Mäuse]],name=[[Birds Of A Feather]],class_level=52,help_en=[[It takes a feather to catch a feather, or so say the hunters of Tailfeather who use the fallen plumes of wild chocobos to fletch their arrows. A fair sum will be paid for any feathers delivered, but beware of bandersnatches lurking in the bushes!]],name_ja=[[アンブロークン・アロー]],},[822]={name_fr=[[Défi: Glawackus Le Gourmand]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Schrecken Der Chocobos]],name=[[Glawackus On, Glawackus Off]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Glawackus─a bandersnatch so greedy it was set upon by its own pack─now wanders the forelands alone, devouring anything it can wrap its claws around...which is most often chocobo hatchlings. Hunt down the beast and slay it once and for all.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[孤高の猛獣「グラワッカス」]],},[823]={name_fr=[[Touche Pas à Nos Saumons]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Bist Du Zu Lax, Gibt's Keinen Lachs]],name=[[Bear Apparent]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Brown bears are eating all the salmon returning upriver to spawn before they can lay their eggs. If this continues, there will be a shortage of harvestable wavekin next season. Bloody the bears' noses so that they might seek sustenance elsewhere.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[サーモン戦争]],},[824]={name_fr=[[Pique-puces De Mossy Peak]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Du Riechst So Gut, Ich Flieg Auf Dich]],name=[[Who's The Moss]],class_level=52,help_en=[[If only poor Mossy Peak had the power to attract Roegadyn maids the way he attracts feather fleas. But he doesn't, and so his only company remains scores of bloodsucking vilekin who, if not dealt with quickly, will suck Mossy Peak dry before he can arrive home.]],name_ja=[[美しく複雑なアロマ]],},[825]={name_fr=[[Sus Aux Hérétiques!]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Urteil Der Furie]],name=[[The Rite Stuff]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Crazed heretics who have forsaken Halone's guidance to befoul their bodies with the blood of the enemy have made a pilgrimage to Mare's Oath─to no doubt perform some horrible pagan rite. Find the mangled creatures, and send their souls to the Fury for final judgment.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[異形の巡礼者]],},[826]={name_fr=[[Vathe-ci Vathe-là]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wir Haben Hunger]],name=[[Dead Meat]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Exiled from the Gnath after losing their ties to the Onemind, the Vath must fare for themselves if they are to survive, and if that means looking to an adventurer for aid in slaying loaghtans, they are not too proud to ask.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[いかにも肉って肉]],},[827]={name_fr=[[Gare à Toi, Hérétique!]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Fanatisch, Didaktisch, Ungut]],name=[[The Whole Truth]],class_level=52,help_en=[[A band of heretics led by the overzealous Huibairten has gathered near Tailfeather, their sights set on the lightly defended hamlet and its bounteous stores of provisions. Slay the wild-eyed men and women before their leader arrives and the assault is commenced.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[敵の敵も敵]],},[828]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Pacification D'Hubairtien]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vorsicht, Bluthochdruck!]],name=[[Nothing But The Truth]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Huibairten is overtaken with madness upon seeing the bodies of his loyal servants strewn across the forest floor. The anger sends his tainted blood a-boiling, hastening his transformation into the beast which now looms before you. Slay the heretic before he sees Tailfeather burn.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[異端の扇動者「熱狂のウベルティアン」]],},[829]={name_fr=[[Repousser Les Gnathes]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Exempel Statuieren]],name=[[Drone Under]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Ever looking to expand the Onemind, the Gnath have sent forth a small parade of drones to seek out and claim new lands. Engage the beastmen and hold the line until the enemy sounds the retreat.]],name_ja=[[戦いを終わらせるもの]],},[830]={name_fr=[[Ça Vathe Mieux Comme ça]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Entscheidung Am Weiland-Fluss]],name=[[El Miacid]],class_level=53,help_en=[[A Vath hates three things, and two of them involve the pesky miacid. Aid the Nonmind in clearing the area of the beastkin and alleviate approximately sixty-seven percent of their worries.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[境界の川]],},[831]={name_fr=[[Bas Les Hippogriffes]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Dracheneierkrieg]],name=[[Cerf's Up]],class_level=53,help_en=[[Not quite a hippogryph and technically not a griffin, the hippocerf is the awkward little cousin in the lion-eagle hybrid family. Ever trying to prove their worth, they engage in reckless behavior that, while oft simply annoying, will sometimes prove deadly, especially when that behavior involves fragile dragon eggs.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[卵をめぐる竜の戦争]],},[832]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'exécution De Svarog]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Svarog Der Schreckliche]],name=[[Elephant In The Brume]],class_level=53,help_en=[[Many a wall in Ishgard's Brume still bear the scars of Svarog's numerous assaults on the city-state proper, as do many a heart of those who have lost kin to the fell wyrm's flames. It is time the deeds were repaid.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[雲霧街の虐殺者「スヴァローグ」]],},[833]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Folie De Migas]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Zorn Einer Mutter]],name=[[The Migas Touch]],class_level=52,help_en=[[Returning from the hunt to find half her clutch being slurped down by a party of hungry Vath has sent nanka matron Migas into a frenzy, and now she threatens to lay waste to all of Loth ast Vath. Assist the Nonmind in pacifying the pond-dweller.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[怒れる母「ミガス」]],},[834]={name_fr=[[Ça Tourne Au Vinaigrier]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Ruf Ihrer Stimmen]],name=[[Hearing Voices]],class_level=53,help_en=[[Scholars claim that the voice of a dragon somehow manipulates the wind aether upon which it is carried─the aether providing the voice with added potency which, in turn, extends range and authority. Heightened vinegaroon activity in the forelands is believed to be in direct correlation with this phenomenon.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[地底の足音]],},[835]={name_fr=[[Défi: Robairlain L'écailleux]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Mourn-Massaker]],name=[[The Mourning After]],class_level=53,help_en=[[The half-man, half-dragon abomination Bloodbearer Robairlain has laid claim to the sacred cavern known as Mourn, slaying several of its peaceful guardians in the process. The Horde and its mindless minions cannot be allowed a foothold so near Ishgardian territories. Find this heretic and expel him from Sohm Al.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[下克上の眷属「竜人のロベルラン」]],},[836]={name_fr=[[Gallimimus En Furie]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Tödliche Hufe]],name=[[Stamp The Yard]],class_level=53,help_en=[[Driven from their territory by Horde dragons, a herd of gallimimuses has begun to stampede. If allowed to reach the forelands' lower elevations, they will most certainly flatten all in their path, from newly planted crops to unsuspecting children. Head off the heated creatures and attempt to slow the rampage.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[殺しが五月蠅くやって来る]],},[837]={name_fr=[[Un Flux De Dragons Fulgurants]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Quell Des Unfriedens]],name=[[Come To My Arms]],class_level=57,help_en=[[A pack of peaceful bandersnatches have begun to clash with several thunder dragons over control of a watering hole. Use the confusion as an opportunity to slay the dragons and calm the bloody waters.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[竜虎の争い]],},[838]={name_fr=[[Défi: Terrasser La Tarasque]],class_level_max=57,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Hasspredigerin]],name=[[Special Tarasque Force]],class_level=53,help_en=[[While rare, the dragon Tarasque will occasionally descend from the Churning Mists to foul the weak minds of heretics seeking truth in the words of the enemy. This opportunity to slay the master manipulator cannot be allowed to slip through our fingers.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[爆着の甲竜「タラスク」]],},[839]={name_fr=[[Des Répulsifs Attirants]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Angriff Der Naschkatzen]],name=[[Mint Condition]],class_level=50,help_en=[[To stave off the myriad vilekin that endlessly nip at the cheeks of the Rose Knights stationed in Cloudtop, several crates filled with seedlings of a natural herb repellent known as catmint were brought in to plant around the camp. Unfortunately, the odor has attracted a clowder of gaelicats who have begun destroying the containers to get at their contents.]],name_ja=[[猫まっしぐら]],},[840]={name_fr=[[Des Oiseaux Soporifiques]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Luftverbessernde Maßnahme]],name=[[Saved The Nests For Last]],class_level=50,help_en=[[The belly of a gastornis is filled with one of the most powerful corrosives known to man, allowing the massive cloudkin to digest almost anything from bones and hair, to crystal and rock. This digestive process produces toxic fumes which are released as the gastornis breathes, making them deadly neighbors...]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[ガストルニスの巣破壊命令]],},[841]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Diatribe De Diatryma]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wir Müssen Mal Reden]],name=[[One Turned Over The Cloudkin's Nest]],class_level=50,help_en=[[If you believed that destroying a giant nest would not upset the giant creature who called that nest home, then Diatryma would like to have a word with you.]],name_ja=[[鮮やかなる丸鳥「ディアトリマ」]],},[842]={name_fr=[[Un Rongeur, Un Volatile, Une Belle Pagaille]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Futterneid]],name=[[Food Fight]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Food is scarce on the floating islets of the Sea of Clouds, so when two species descend on the same hunting grounds, chaos is bound to erupt. That chaos, however, can be a blessing in disguise by providing an opportunity to kill two birds (or more accurately one bird and one rodent-like creature) with one stone.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[雲海の大乱闘]],},[843]={name_fr=[[Hirudothérapie Géante]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Eine Frage Der Größe]],name=[[Leech The Sky]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Not a soul in the realm would deny that a good leeching now and again keeps the humours clean and the body free of sickness, but pumpkin-sized leeches capable of rendering a man into a husk in a matter of moments? That is a different story altogether.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[薔薇の血を吸いたくて]],},[844]={name_fr=[[Et Zou, Plus D'anzus !]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Früh übt Sich, Oder Auch Nicht]],name=[[Anzu Trois]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Once anzu hatchlings reach a certain age, their mothers will begin taking them hunting so that the hatchlings can learn the art of subduing prey. Slay the birds, both young and old, to prevent the fostering of new killers.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[黒い鳥]],},[845]={name_fr=[[La Guerre Des Gundu]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Übermut Der Jungen Gundo]],name=[[Youth Must Be Severed]],class_level=50,help_en=[[As a display of strength, young members of the Gundu tribe will taunt their enemies using petty acts of aggression such as shouting insults or throwing feces. Those especially brave and arrogant, however, will actually physically attack, and without someone to bloody their noses, the violence can only escalate.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[若気の至り]],},[846]={name_fr=[[Défi: De Haut En Bas]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Langer Fall]],name=[[A Long Way Down]],class_level=50,help_en=[[The paissas are a mischievous bunch, finding amusement in cracking open Rose Knight crates and tossing their contents off Cloudtop to the ground thousands of yalms below. The worst offender─a deceptively adorable misfit named Apotamkin─has been sighted, and the order is out to show him the same fate as the crates.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[不法投棄者「アポタムキン」]],},[847]={name_fr=[[Jeter La Première Pierre]],class_level_max=54,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Eindruck Schinden]],name=[[This Is How We Gundu]],class_level=50,help_en=[[Armed warriors of the hostile Gundu tribe have gathered before Vundu Ok' Bendu and begun the ritual hooting of insults and stomping of talons which normally serve as a prelude to battle. Rather than wait for the Vanu to attack, the Rose Knights have elected to cast the first stone.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[雲海の戦士]],},[851]={name_fr=[[Un Abus De Demainsels]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Böses Erwachen]],name=[[Come To My Window]],class_level=57,help_en=[[One too many puffs on the morrowmote pipe put the Zundu tribe wamourakeeper's mind so at ease that he forgot to lock the gate to the silk pens before retiring to bed. When he woke the next morning to the chaos inflicted by the escaped moths, he wondered why the morrowmotes did not provide him with visions of this particular future.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[素晴らしい新世界]],},[852]={name_fr=[[Des Noyaux Désaltérants]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Kern Des Problems]],name=[[Obey Their Thirst]],class_level=57,help_en=[[The Zundu tribe discovered long ago that the hearts of cloud sprites are crystals which, when shattered, expel large amounts of clean, drinkable water─a resource quite scarce on their floating islets. The problem is removing the hearts from their owners who, annoyingly enough, require them to live.]],name_ja=[[空の上の雲]],},[853]={name_fr=[[Le Repose-pieds Fugitif]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Im Schweiße Seiner Hühneraugen]],name=[[The Fugitive]],class_level=57,help_en=[[A young member of the Zundu tribe, kidnapped and forced to serve as a footrest for a Vundu elder, has escaped his captors and is trying to return home. The elder, displeased that his favorite footrest has flown the coop, has gathered a small army to search every cookhouse, birdhouse, and outhouse in order to reclaim what he rightfully abducted.]],name_ja=[[逃亡者]],},[854]={name_fr=[[Le Repose-pieds Pris à Contre-pied]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ein Vundo Lässt Nicht Locker]],name=[[Zuns On The Run]],class_level=57,help_en=[[The warrior who kindly agreed to escort the former footrest back to the Zundu village has turned out to be a gaelicat's-paw of the Vundu elder who kidnapped the young Zundu. It appears that boy will require further escort if he is ever to arrive home.]],name_ja=[[追跡者]],},[855]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mangeur De Terre Gardée]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wider Die Eigene Natur]],name=[[On Dangerous Ground]],class_level=57,help_en=[[After centuries of protecting the land, one groundskeeper had enough and began devouring the very stuff he was tasked with defending. Decommission the groundseater before there are no islets left in the sky.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[暴食の岩人形「グランズイーター」]],},[856]={name_fr=[[Des Durs En Cuir]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Gebt Her Euer Leder]],name=[[Leather And Mace]],class_level=57,help_en=[[Tanning techniques are relatively unknown to the Vanu Vanu, making treated leather a rare commodity in the Sea of Clouds. Rather than learn to make their own, some of the tribes would instead forcefully take it from the area's new arrivals clad head to toe in the protective wear.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[補給線を断て]],},[857]={name_fr=[[Les Ennemis De Mes Ennemis...]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Trimm Zwei]],name=[[Hearts Like Steel, Fists Like Thunder]],class_level=57,help_en=[[Soldiers of the VIth Imperial Legion have engaged with the Vundu tribe. Allow the two sides to weaken each other, then sneak in and claim the heads of both.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[招かれざる客]],},[860]={name_fr=[[Défi: Il Y A Un Os à Plume]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Die Knochenjägerin]],name=[[Bones]],class_level=57,help_en=[[Though average Vanu lifespans would suggest she is not a day over thirty summers, members of the Zundu claim that Vundu warrioress Oonu Vali has been collecting the bones of her victims and adding them to her feathers since the dawn of time.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[恐怖の対象「積乱のオヌバリ」]],},[861]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'incantateur Des Brumes]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Primae Müssen Draußen Bleiben]],name=[[Bismarcking Time]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Vundu high priest Kena Vanu has begun a forbidden rite which, if allowed to continue, will summon forth the very Lord of the Mists, Bismarck. Slay the beastman and prevent certain tragedy.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[雲神の司祭「入道のケナバヌ」]],},[862]={name_fr=[[Les Acolytes De L'incantateur]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Rache Für Kena Vanu]],name=[[Let There Be Acolytes]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Acolytes of the temporarily dispatched Kena Vanu have sworn revenge on the featherless netherlings who silenced their master before he could finish teaching them all seventy-three mysteries of the skies.]],name_ja=[[ケナバヌの弟子たち]],},[863]={name_fr=[[Défi: L'incantateur Des Brumes Revient]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Priester Mit Dem Vogel]],name=[[A Disturbing Lack Of Faith]],class_level=59,help_en=[[It appears Kena Vanu was not as thoroughly dispatched as originally believed, and the high priest has returned, not with the Lord of the Mists, but with a creature almost as imposing at his side. Ware the impaling talons of the dread Skvader and slay the beastman who summoned him.]],name_ja=[[復讐の司祭「入道のケナバヌ」]],},[864]={name_fr=[[Alerte Aux Bombardements Aériens]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Erspart Uns Den Mist]],name=[[Guano A Mano]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Nothing is worse than finding yourself underneath a flock of toco tocos as they relieve themselves of their recent meals...until you realize that toco toco guano is highly corrosive and can burn your flesh down to the bone. Disperse the converging cloudkin before they carpet bomb the entire area with their fetid feces.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[絨毯爆撃]],},[865]={name_fr=[[Défi: Podarge Au Pot]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Wahnsinn Vorprogrammiert]],name=[[The Sound Of Madness]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Vanu tribes claim that the shrill mating call of Podarge, a fearsome cloudkin who inhabits the Sea of Clouds, can drive men to madness─the most severely affected throwing themselves off islands simply to escape the terrible sound. Silence the creature before your own sanity is lost.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[狂気の歌声「ポダルゲー」]],},[866]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dans Les Griffes D'Akhekhu]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Vanu Mit Soße]],name=[[You Eat What You Aren't]],class_level=59,help_en=[[The diet of a griffin is believed to consist mostly of the flesh of small- to medium-sized mountain creatures such as goats and gaelicats. The hulking Akhekhu, however, will only sup on fully grown Vanu Vanu, making the cloudkin both hated and feared by the islet tribes.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[雲海の狂風「アケク」]],},[867]={name_fr=[[Oiseaux Peu Lyriques]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Die Traumfresser]],name=[[A Dream, Perchance To Eat]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Some Vanu Vanu tribes believe that one's soul leaves the body every night to journey to the realm of dreams. It is also believed that cloudkin known as tsanahales will perch atop village huts in an attempt to devour these souls, making the creatures hated across the Sea of Clouds.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[不吉な鳥は雲の彼方へ飛ぶ]],},[868]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sus à Sombrécaille]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Dunkelschuppe I: Ein Drache Dreht Auf]],name=[[Darkscale Descendeth]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Vowing to see Zenith suffer no more at the ravaging claws of the Horde, Hraesvelgr has summoned the mighty Vedrfolnir to do his bidding. Join the white dragon in defending the ancient spire from Darkscale─one of Nidhogg's most fearsome generals.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[ダークスケール征討戦：白竜支援]],},[869]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sombrécaille Se Soigne]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Dunkelschuppe II: Ein Drache Dreht Ab]],name=[[Darkscale Disappeareth]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Both body and pride wounded, Darkscale has ordered his three captains to guard his retreat from Zenith. Focus your efforts on the minions before the healing properties of the general's dragon blood see him to a full recovery.]],name_ja=[[ダークスケール征討戦：追撃作戦]],},[870]={name_fr=[[Défi: Quand Sombre Sombrécaille]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Dunkelschuppe III: Ein Drache Gibt Den Löffel Ab]],name=[[Darkscale Devoureth]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Tapping into the aetherial energy of a nearby crystal deposit has filled Darkscale with newfound strength. Engage the unyielding dragon in one last battle to the death.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[ダークスケール征討戦：総力決戦]],},[871]={name_fr=[[Défi: Duel Amical Contre Vedrfolnir]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ehrenduell Mit Dem Weißen]],name=[[Vedrfolnir Devoteth]],class_level=56,help_en=[[Thoroughly impressed with your valor in the slaying of Darkscale, Vedrfolnir has granted you a boon─the honor of matching strength on the field of battle with the white dragon himself.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[蒼天の白竜「ヴェズルフェルニル」]],},[872]={name_fr=[[Garde De Bébé Dragon]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Aufpassdrachenkind]],name=[[End Of The Rainbow]],class_level=54,help_en=[[It appears curiosity is not only suited for killing cats, but dragon pups as well. An ill-advised adventure far from his den has placed Rhei End in the face of imminent danger. Hurry to the pup in peril and see that his inquisitive nature is not the end of him.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[白亜の宮殿防衛戦：子竜救援]],},[873]={name_fr=[[Sus Aux Sous-fifres!]],class_level_max=59,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Rastabans Rage]],name=[[Rastaban Vibration]],class_level=55,help_en=[[Led by Darkscale's trusted Captain Rastaban, a sizable knot of dragons has begun advancing towards Zenith. Slay Rastaban's minions and put an end to the assault before it can begin.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[白亜の宮殿防衛戦：猛竜討伐]],},[874]={name_fr=[[Défi: Touche Pas Mes Mogs]],class_level_max=58,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Sadistische Spiele]],name=[[Mogicide]],class_level=54,help_en=[[Another of Darkscale's captains has launched an assault on Zenith, but instead of focusing his attacks on the spire itself, the dragon seeks to slaughter Zenith's moogle caretakers.]],map={placename={name=[[The Churning Mists]],},},name_ja=[[白亜の宮殿防衛戦：モーグリ救援]],},[875]={name_fr=[[Défi: Clouer Le Bec à Yehl]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Der Schrecken Der Lüfte]],name=[[Rebel Yehl]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Incensed by the recent influx of free company airships into its territory, the savage cloudkin Yehl has declared a one-bird war on any and all denizens of the lower realm.]],map={placename={name=[[The Sea Of Clouds]],},},name_ja=[[大嘴の怪鳥「イェル」]],},[877]={name_fr=[[Proto-Ultima: La Menace Surgie Du Passé]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ultima: Ein Prototyp Tankt Auf]],name=[[Prey Online]],class_level=59,help_en=[[After five millennia offline, Proto Ultima has restored auxiliary power and begun a full systems check. To recharge its main power cells, the Allagan killing machine has deployed several aether collectors guarded by some of the most frightening of the fallen empire's godless creations.]],name_ja=[[太古の脅威：ノクチルカ撃滅戦]],},[878]={name_fr=[[Proto-Ultima: La Menace Surgie Du Passé]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ultima: Ein Prototyp Tankt Auf]],name=[[Prey Online]],class_level=59,help_en=[[After five millennia offline, Proto Ultima has restored auxiliary power and begun a full systems check. To recharge its main power cells, the Allagan killing machine has deployed several aether collectors guarded by some of the most frightening of the fallen empire's godless creations.]],name_ja=[[太古の脅威：ノクチルカ撃滅戦]],},[879]={name_fr=[[Proto-Ultima: La Menace Surgie Du Passé]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ultima: Ein Prototyp Tankt Auf]],name=[[Prey Online]],class_level=59,help_en=[[After five millennia offline, Proto Ultima has restored auxiliary power and begun a full systems check. To recharge its main power cells, the Allagan killing machine has deployed several aether collectors guarded by some of the most frightening of the fallen empire's godless creations.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[太古の脅威：ノクチルカ撃滅戦]],},[880]={name_fr=[[1001 Circuits Morts]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Lockere Schrauben]],name=[[A Bug's Death]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Several verification nodes have identified a unit of malfunctioning clockwork engineers and are requesting assistance in the deactivation of the faulty machina.]],name_ja=[[バグ報告ナンバー壱九九]],},[881]={name_fr=[[Fuite Tardive]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wir Packen Unseren Koffer]],name=[[The Late Escape]],class_level=59,help_en=[[A slither of self-aware lamiae are attempting an escape from Azys Lla. If the biologically engineered warriors were able to reach Eorzea, the realm would run red with the blood of their victims. Stop the lamiae before they can reach Helix.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[輪廻の蛇]],},[882]={name_fr=[[Défi: Des Frasques à La Défrag']],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Fürst Und Der Richter]],name=[[Still Ticking]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Unauthorized personnel (you!) have been detected in the Alpha Quadrant and a clockwork defragmentation unit has been deployed to neutralize the threat.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[アラグ脅威のメカニズム]],},[883]={name_fr=[[Défi: Euthanasie Cérébrale]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Hungriges Hirn]],name=[[Life Of Brain]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Thousands of years of uncontrolled reproduction and mutation have seen one chimera's cranial capacity nearly double, resulting in a creature too clever...and deadly for its own good. Slay the chimera brain, and end its line.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[狡知の魔獣「キマイラブレイン」]],},[884]={name_fr=[[Une Masse De Monstres]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Empusen-Epidemie]],name=[[The Monster Mass]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Ages of neglect have taken their toll on the functionality of the equipment housed in the Biomass Incubation Complex. A malfunction has caused the machines to awaken and begin the mass regeneration of empuses─hideous creatures engineered to kill.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[魔獣狩り]],},[885]={name_fr=[[Défi: Couchée, Sale Bête !]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Blinde Wut]],name=[[Pet, Smart]],class_level=59,help_en=[[A favorite pet of Emperor Xande, the artificially cloned voidsent Muchalinda has been out of temper since the death of her master, and now believes she knows upon who she might place the blame.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[忠義の妖王「ムチャリンダ」]],},[886]={name_fr=[[Des Plantes Monstres]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Giftgrüne Daumen]],name=[[The Root Of Evil]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Water is a scarce resource on the corrupted islands of Azys Lla. To survive, the few plants which grow in the area must extend their roots to any sort of moisture available...even if that includes the chemically enriched incubation fluid in which chimeras are grown.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ミュータントフラワーズ]],},[887]={name_fr=[[Gare à L'avant-garde]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Wehe, Wenn Sie Alleingelassen]],name=[[The Mystery Machine]],class_level=59,help_en=[[In an attempt to bypass Allagan security, the VIth Imperial Legion has off-loaded a small army of magitek vanguards L-1 from their dreadnaught and deployed them throughout the Gamma Quadrant. While their main targets are clockwork sentries, the machina could pose a deterrent for the allies of Eorzea. Deactivate the machina and cast the rubble to the lands below.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[スチールシティ]],},[888]={name_fr=[[Guerre Technologique]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Das Bleibt Lieber Vergessen]],name=[[Rampant Speculation]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Imperial speculators are scouring the Gamma Quadrant for military technology that they may take back to Garlemald and incorporate into their armies. Stop the imperials before they can report to the Gration.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ロストテクノロジー]],},[889]={name_fr=[[Bas Les Griffes]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Alle Klauen Voll Zu Tun]],name=[[Put The Knives Down]],class_level=59,help_en=[[When not used to tear enemies of the Empire limb from limb, adamantite claws are often employed at construction sites for digging holes, demolishing old buildings, and lifting objects. Here, they seem intent on tearing you limb from limb.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[全自動手作業]],},[890]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mettre Sylla à Mal]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Chef Ist Sauer]],name=[[Scared Sylla]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Senior magitek technician Sylla mal Albinus has arrived from Garlemald to conduct his inspection of the location chosen for the construction of Castrum Solus. Act quickly, for a similar chance to apprehend the high-ranking imperial official may not present itself again.]],name_ja=[[魔導技師長「シラ・マル・アルビヌス」]],},[891]={name_fr=[[Recadrer Le Quadrant Est]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vertreibung Aus Gamma-Ost]],name=[[Phi Slamma Gamma East]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Seeking to lay claim to the area before the Eorzean Alliance, the VIth Imperial Legion has dispatched several centuries of soldiers to secure footholds in strategic locations throughout the Gamma Quadrant.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ガンマ戦線バースト：東部]],},[892]={name_fr=[[Recadrer Le Quadrant Ouest]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vertreibung Aus Gamma-West]],name=[[Phi Slamma Gamma West]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Seeking to lay claim to the area before the Eorzean Alliance, the VIth Imperial Legion has dispatched several centuries of soldiers to secure footholds in strategic locations throughout the Gamma Quadrant.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ガンマ戦線バースト：西部]],},[893]={name_fr=[[Recadrer Le Quadrant Sud]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Vertreibung Aus Gamma-Süd]],name=[[Phi Slamma Gamma South]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Seeking to lay claim to the area before the Eorzean Alliance, the VIth Imperial Legion has dispatched several centuries of soldiers to secure footholds in strategic locations throughout the Gamma Quadrant.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ガンマ戦線バースト：南部]],},[894]={name_fr=[[Yak à Le Faire]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Tödliche Unzurechnungsfähigkeit]],name=[[Yak It Up]],class_level=59,help_en=[[The Allagan Empire is infamous for its wanton manipulation of the gods' creations─the Meracydian brobinyak being only one of many examples. Put these pitiful creatures out of their misery and restore nature's equilibrium.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[無知性化の嵐]],},[895]={name_fr=[[Défi: Décapitation De Goryschche]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Feuer Mit Feuer Bekämpfen]],name=[[No Greater Goryshche]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Even the mighty dragons themselves were subject to the Allagan Empire's incessant tinkering with the very laws of nature─Goryshche is one such product of that imperial hubris. Aimlessly roaming the Azys Lla wastes, the multi-headed abomination silently seeks an end to five thousand years of suffering.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[人造多頭竜「ゴリシュチェ」]],},[897]={name_fr=[[Alerte Dans Le Vide]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Ernter Des Todes]],name=[[Harvest Moon]],class_level=59,help_en=[[An alarum blares from some unknown source, accompanied by the following message: “Administrative node malfunction! Unit deployment error. Automatic recall failed. Removal request submitted. Authorization code 5670-2H5BB-Q90. Repeat. Administrative node malfunction...”]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[大量誤発注事件]],},[898]={name_fr=[[Défi: Sthéno En Quarantaine]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Stheno Abschreiben]],name=[[Out Of Sight, Out Of Mind]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Data retrieved from tomestones discovered in the Delta Quadrant provide proof that the chimerical failure codenamed Stheno was one of the reasons the quarantine block was originally constructed.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[不吉なる実験体「ステンノー」]],},[899]={name_fr=[[Traitement D'amphiptère]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Seelenlose Grausamkeit]],name=[[A Room Without Books]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Extensive manipulation of not only the body, but the mind, has left most of the Allagans' creations soulless horrors who only act upon instinct. The Meracydian amphiptere will simply kill without thought as to why it does so, death being the only cure to its disease.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[魂なき肉体のごとし]],},[900]={name_fr=[[Reptoïdes Tueurs à Tuer]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Reptilische Rächer]],name=[[Curiously Strong Things]],class_level=59,help_en=[[While it is unclear how they were utilized in battle, it is clear from their muscular build and violent disposition that reptoids were designed for one purpose, and one purpose only─killing.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[ハイアラガンユーザー]],},[901]={name_fr=[[Défi: Les Drilles Rêvent-ils De Meules électriques ?]],class_level_max=63,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Der Rotierende Turm Von Azys Lla]],name=[[Do Spinners Dream Of Electric Rooks]],class_level=59,help_en=[[Severed communication with spinner-rooks under its administrative control has prompted the emergence of the spinner-rick to assess the problem. Destroy the node and deal a blow to the quadrant's rook activity.]],map={placename={name=[[Azys Lla]],},},name_ja=[[夢見る無人機「リックスピナー」]],},[902]={name_fr=[[Défi: Mort à La Reine Des Coeurls]],class_level_max=56,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Angriff Der Königin]],name=[[Long Live The Coeurl]],class_level=52,help_en=[[The queen of the coeurls has declared war on Tailfeather and leads an assault on the settlement and its inhabitants. Confront Her Majesty and deliver the kiss of regicide.]],name_ja=[[雷獣の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[903]={name_fr=[[Défi: Du Coeurl à L'ouvrage]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Rückkehr Der Königin]],name=[[Coeurls Chase Boys]],class_level=57,help_en=[[It appears Coeurlregina's first attack on Tailfeather was naught more than a calculated feint to gauge the collective strength of those defending the hamlet. Now privy to the settlement's weaknesses, she returns with her army's true strength.]],name_ja=[[逆襲の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[904]={name_fr=[[Défi: Du Coeurl à L'ouvrage]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Rückkehr Der Königin]],name=[[Coeurls Chase Boys]],class_level=57,help_en=[[It appears Coeurlregina's first attack on Tailfeather was naught more than a calculated feint to gauge the collective strength of those defending the hamlet. Now privy to the settlement's weaknesses, she returns with her army's true strength.]],name_ja=[[逆襲の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[905]={name_fr=[[Défi: Coeurls Brisés]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Entmachtung Der Königin]],name=[[Coeurls Chase Boys Chase Coeurls]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Her main offensive a tactical failure, Coeurlregina has sounded the retreat. However, if allowed the luxury of escape, it will only be a matter of time before the wicked beast is conspiring another assault. Make chase, and end the queen's reign here and now.]],name_ja=[[幻影の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[906]={name_fr=[[Défi: Coeurls Brisés]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Entmachtung Der Königin]],name=[[Coeurls Chase Boys Chase Coeurls]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Her main offensive a tactical failure, Coeurlregina has sounded the retreat. However, if allowed the luxury of escape, it will only be a matter of time before the wicked beast is conspiring another assault. Make chase, and end the queen's reign here and now.]],name_ja=[[幻影の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[907]={name_fr=[[Défi: Coeurls Brisés]],class_level_max=255,patch={number=[[3.0]],},name_de=[[Entmachtung Der Königin]],name=[[Coeurls Chase Boys Chase Coeurls]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Her main offensive a tactical failure, Coeurlregina has sounded the retreat. However, if allowed the luxury of escape, it will only be a matter of time before the wicked beast is conspiring another assault. Make chase, and end the queen's reign here and now.]],name_ja=[[幻影の女王「クァールレギナ」]],},[908]={name_fr=[[De La Glace à Piler!]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Eiskalte Killer]],name=[[Sphenopalatine Ganglioneuralgia]],class_level=56,help_en=[[The change in climate experienced by Coerthas after the fall of Dalamud has done more than freeze rivers and prevent the growth of foliage─it has made the region more hospitable for a myriad of terrible creatures normally only found dwelling atop the highest of mountains─creatures that have proven naught but headaches for the residents of the western highlands.]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[アイスクリーム頭痛]],},[909]={name_fr=[[Défi: Stihi, C'est Fini!]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Der Erzfeind Der Vollstrecker]],name=[[A Stihi Situation]],class_level=56,help_en=[[There are very few dragons the Convictors do not dream of slaying─the cold and calculating Stihi being no exception. The knights, however, while skilled at dreaming, have been less than successful at actually subduing the creature...]],map={placename={name=[[Coerthas Western Highlands]],},},name_ja=[[冷酷なる氷竜「スティヒ」]],},[910]={name_fr=[[Défi: La Vierge Marrie]],class_level_max=61,patch={number=[[3.01]],},name_de=[[Drachenmaid, Hast Du Heut Für Mich Zeit]],name=[[Ware The Maiden Fair]],class_level=57,help_en=[[Once a beautiful young Elezen with skin like snow and hair like an autumn sun, the dragon maiden was driven to sip the blood of the Horde after being set upon by a pair of highborn knights (who were subsequently tried and hung for their crimes). Since then, she has grown into one of the most ruthless of all wyrm-blooded heretics, attacking even innocent children. Deliver the maiden from this world and give her soul peace once again.]],map={placename={name=[[The Dravanian Forelands]],},},name_ja=[[変貌せし乙女「ドラゴンメイデン」]],},[911]={name_fr=[[Corriger Les Bugs]],class_level_max=14,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Wiederkehrende Bugs]],name=[[Recurring Bugs]],class_level=9,help_en=[[A swarm of mechanical monstrosities is wreaking havoc on the environs of Thanalan. Stand together with the wandering minstrel, and eradicate this skittering threat.]],name_ja=[[バグフィックス]],},[912]={name_fr=[[Corriger Les Bugs]],class_level_max=14,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Wiederkehrende Bugs]],name=[[Recurring Bugs]],class_level=9,help_en=[[A swarm of mechanical monstrosities is wreaking havoc on the environs of Thanalan. Stand together with the wandering minstrel, and eradicate this skittering threat.]],name_ja=[[バグフィックス]],},[913]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Regard Froid Du Mamool Ja]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Eins, Zwei, Sittenpolizei]],name=[[The Sarong Song]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Faires attract all sorts, and one Mamool Ja has been so incensed by the sights and sounds that he insists on showing the dance of his people, which would make even the most ribald pirate blush. Drive the overeager Mamool Ja away and protect the sensibilities of the beach's faire-goers.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「良俗の守護者」]],},[914]={name_fr=[[Ce N'est Qu'un Amour De Vacances]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Verrückt Nach Dir]],name=[[The Belle Of The Beach]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Pirates often spend moons surrounded by nothing but frigid seawater, and the appearance of this lovely courtesan has set their hearts aflame with passion. Quell the surging tide of unwanted attention so she can enjoy her vacation in peace.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「一夏の熱狂」]],},[915]={name_fr=[[Jouer Avec Le Feu]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Zündeln Verboten]],name=[[Sparking Up The Wrong Beach]],class_level=30,help_en=[[A group of pirates have decided to celebrate their own way by bringing a cart filled with fireworks of suspect quality to the beach. Drive them away before their explosives harm any innocent faire-goers.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「危険な火遊び」]],},[916]={name_fr=[[Défi: Dressé Contre Son Maître]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Seeungeheuer Bitte Anleinen]],name=[[It Came From Beneath The Deep]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Certain beasts, when properly trained, can provide endless entertainment to spectators, but when they start running amok─as this one has─they must needs be put down. Slay the trained Thing from the Deep before it harms any innocent onlookers.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「海獣の調教師」]],},[917]={name_fr=[[Dragueurs De Bac à Sable]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Badelust, Badefrust]],name=[[Life's A Beach]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Two faire-goers wishing to enjoy the fireworks in peace are being accosted by a group of insistent pirates. Teach the pirates to respect the wishes of others, and be prepared if they decide not to listen.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「軟派者の末路」]],},[918]={name_fr=[[Des Bouteilles à La Mer]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.07]],},name_de=[[Und Ne Buddel Voll Rum]],name=[[Feeling Groggy]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Pirates wishing to keep their own festivities going have brought a supply of liquor, causing a scene and littering the beach with bottles. Collect the bottles by force and pick up any you find on the ground to keep the pirates from causing any more trouble.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「海賊の密造酒」]],},[932]={name_fr=[[Crabes Martyrs]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Räuber Mit Den Scherenhänden]],name=[[Our Favorite Pastime]],class_level=30,help_en=[[To begin her training, Iroha would challenge the robber crabs of Costa del Sol. Fight by her side and see that she is not overwhelmed.]],name_ja=[[星唄異聞：あなたの為に]],},[933]={name_fr=[[De L'excellence Du Samouraï]],class_level_max=36,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Der Weg Des Samurai]],name=[[The Way Of The Samurai]],class_level=31,help_en=[[Iroha is surprised to find that the voidsent near Haukke Manor are reminiscent of demons from an old story she knows well. Join her in battle and help her to defeat the fiends.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[星唄異聞：偉大な侍の証]],},[934]={name_fr=[[Un Scorpion Pas Si Pacifique]],class_level_max=37,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Skorpione Beißen Nicht]],name=[[Serket Breaker]],class_level=32,help_en=[[While investigating rumors of a sinister creature, Iroha finds herself face-to-face with Serket, a fearsome beast of legend. Join forces with Iroha and see if the monstrosity lives up to its reputation.]],map={placename={name=[[Southern Thanalan]],},},name_ja=[[星唄異聞：計り知れない強敵]],},[935]={name_fr=[[Le Secret D'Amatsu: Kyôri]],class_level_max=38,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Der Schlüssel Zu Amatsu Kyori]],name=[[The Key To Amatsu: Kyori]],class_level=33,help_en=[[With her memories restored, the time has come for Iroha to wield Amatsu: Kyori in battle. Help her to defeat the dread dragon and its voidsent minion that she might harness the power within.]],map={placename={name=[[Upper La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[星唄異聞：「鏡裏」の極意]],},[936]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=5,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[937]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=18,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=13,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[938]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=5,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],map={placename={name=[[Middle La Noscea]],},},name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[939]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=20,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=15,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[940]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=16,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=11,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],map={placename={name=[[Central Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[941]={name_fr=[[Le Mochi, ça Rend Marteau!]],class_level_max=11,patch={number=[[3.1]],},name_de=[[Reis Stampfen, Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding Rice, Pounding Hearts]],class_level=6,help_en=[[There is no mochi as tasty as that pounded by the mallet of an overzealous cyclops. Nimble adventurers are needed to retrieve advent cakes from the Heavensturn mortar while avoiding any monkey mischief.]],map={placename={name=[[North Shroud]],},},name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅持ち逃げろ！」]],},[942]={name_fr=[[Chasse Aux Prœufs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.2]],},name_de=[[Fröhliche Eiersuche]],name=[[Eggstract And Eggspedite]],class_level=1,help_en=[[Seeking to recapture a lucid dream she had, Jihli Aliapoh has hidden Archon eggs throughout the quarter and employed her most restless spriggan to oversee a frivolous hunt. Snatch up as many as you can and deliver them to the spriggan before the hunt ends as abruptly as the dream did.]],name_ja=[[エッグハント「集めろ飾りタマゴ」]],},[943]={name_fr=[[Chasse Aux Prœufs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.2]],},name_de=[[Fröhliche Eiersuche]],name=[[Eggstract And Eggspedite]],class_level=1,help_en=[[Seeking to recapture a lucid dream she had, Jihli Aliapoh has hidden Archon eggs throughout the quarter and employed her most restless spriggan to oversee a frivolous hunt. Snatch up as many as you can and deliver them to the spriggan before the hunt ends as abruptly as the dream did.]],name_ja=[[エッグハント「集めろ飾りタマゴ」]],},[944]={name_fr=[[Chasse Aux Prœufs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.2]],},name_de=[[Fröhliche Eiersuche]],name=[[Eggstract And Eggspedite]],class_level=1,help_en=[[Seeking to recapture a lucid dream she had, Jihli Aliapoh has hidden Archon eggs throughout the quarter and employed her most restless spriggan to oversee a frivolous hunt. Snatch up as many as you can and deliver them to the spriggan before the hunt ends as abruptly as the dream did.]],name_ja=[[エッグハント「集めろ飾りタマゴ」]],},[945]={name_fr=[[Pourvu Que Les Méchants Perdent!]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.35]],},name_de=[[Heiße Gewässer]],name=[[In Deep Water]],class_level=30,help_en=[[Bombards have begun creeping ashore and must be prevented from moving any further inland. While the Go Go Posing Rangers─heroes tasked with ridding the realm of the Bombard King and his minions─see to some last-minute preparations, their allies must rise to the occasion. Beat back the fiends with the waters of an elbst and wait for the Rangers to arrive.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「襲来 ボンバード！」]],},[946]={name_fr=[[Pourvu Que Les Gentils Gagnent!]],class_level_max=35,patch={number=[[3.35]],},name_de=[[Die Rückkehr Des Königs]],name=[[Trial By Fire]],class_level=30,help_en=[[The Go Go Posing Rangers have arrived but there is no end to the battalion of burgeoning Bombards summoned by their king and for every one of the flaming voidsent extinguished, another pops up in its place. Keep the Rangers out of harm's way by blasting the tiny fiends with elbst water.]],name_ja=[[紅蓮祭「登場 火消しの戦士！」]],},[959]={name_fr=[[Pour Une Poignée De Mochi]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[3.45]],},name_de=[[Mehr Reis Stampfen, Mehr Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding More Mochi, Pounding More Hearts]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Ravenous birds have been flocking to the pounding site and wolfing down all the freshly pounded mochi. Retrieve what you can of the advent cakes before there is nothing left to distribute to festival-goers.]],name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅取り逃げろ！」]],},[960]={name_fr=[[Pour Une Poignée De Mochi]],class_level_max=18,patch={number=[[3.45]],},name_de=[[Mehr Reis Stampfen, Mehr Herzen Erobern]],name=[[Pounding More Mochi, Pounding More Hearts]],class_level=13,help_en=[[Ravenous birds have been flocking to the pounding site and wolfing down all the freshly pounded mochi. Retrieve what you can of the advent cakes before there is nothing left to distribute to festival-goers.]],name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅取り逃げろ！」]],},[961]={name_fr=[[Ce Mochi A Du Chien]],class_level_max=10,patch={number=[[4.15]],},name_de=[[Kampfhunde Von Der Leine Gelassen]],name=[[Who Let The Hounds Out]],class_level=5,help_en=[[Pirates bent on disrupting the Heavensturn celebration have loosed their deckhounds at the mochi pounding site. Adventurers must doggedly retrieve advent cakes while contending with the savage beasts.]],name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅取り逃げろ！」]],},[962]={name_fr=[[Ce Mochi A Du Chien]],class_level_max=18,patch={number=[[4.15]],},name_de=[[Kampfhunde Von Der Leine Gelassen]],name=[[Who Let The Hounds Out]],class_level=13,help_en=[[Pirates bent on disrupting the Heavensturn celebration have loosed their deckhounds at the mochi pounding site. Adventurers must doggedly retrieve advent cakes while contending with the savage beasts.]],name_ja=[[降神祭「モチモチ餅取り逃げろ！」]],},[963]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[964]={name_fr=[[Dévouement Aveugle]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Riskante Unternehmungen]],name=[[Mad Ventures In Retainer-sitting]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Not content with the paltry pickings his retainer was retrieving from ventures into the Black Shroud, a well-to-do noble recently ordered his humble hireling to the Diadem, forbidding the retainer's return until “treasure worthy of a king” was discovered. All the poor soul discovered, however, was a den of starving sky creatures, and now requires aid in escape.]],name_ja=[[無謀すぎた探索]],},[965]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[966]={name_fr=[[Le Parfum Enivrant De L'éther]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Im Schatten Von Kerkes]],name=[[Prepare For Gory]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Drawn to the Diadem by the islands' extreme concentrations of ambient aether, the carnivorous kerkes strikes fear into all who lay eyes upon it─the kerkes, whose wingspan is so large, its feathers blot out the sun. So prepare to fight in the shade.]],name_ja=[[大雲海を行く渡り鳥]],},[967]={name_fr=[[Le Parfum Enivrant De L'éther]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Im Schatten Von Kerkes]],name=[[Prepare For Gory]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Drawn to the Diadem by the islands' extreme concentrations of ambient aether, the carnivorous kerkes strikes fear into all who lay eyes upon it─the kerkes, whose wingspan is so large, its feathers blot out the sun. So prepare to fight in the shade.]],name_ja=[[大雲海を行く渡り鳥]],},[968]={name_fr=[[Défi: Brachiosaures En Famille]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Geheimnis Der Verschollenen Legende]],name=[[Secret Of The Lost Legend]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Responding to the cries of her child, a mother brachiosaur has launched a merciless attack on a band of adventurers who entered the Diadem looking to capture a baby brachiosaur and return with it to Ishgard where they would auction it to the highest bidder.]],name_ja=[[星呼の古代獣「ブラキオレイドス」]],},[969]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[970]={name_fr=[[Petit, Un Jour Tu Ne Seras Pas Grand]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Ende Der Verschollenen Legende]],name=[[Slaughter Of The Lost Legend]],class_level=60,help_en=[[From out of the morning mist emerge harmless baby brachiosaurs─gentle, well-tempered, kind...yet, allowed to mature to full size and these innocent infants could claim the lives of countless. How exactly that might happen remains to be seen, but orders are orders.]],name_ja=[[恐竜伝説ベイビー]],},[971]={name_fr=[[Défi: Le Serpent Aux écailles D'argent]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Tödliche Umarmung]],name=[[Embrace Of The Serpent]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Once again, a band of wide-eyed adventurers have bitten off slightly more than they can chew by attempting to capture a basilosaurus─a silver-scaled serpent that can grow to over two score fulms in length from fiery forked tongue to tail.]],name_ja=[[銀鱗の雲海蛇「バシロサウルス」]],},[972]={name_fr=[[La Brise De Pierre]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Das Pelikan-Problem]],name=[[The Pelican Grief]],class_level=60,help_en=[[To subdue their prey, crown pelicans expel from their beaks a fine mist containing a powerful toxin capable of lithifying flesh. The problem is, much of this discharge is carried off by the wind before striking the intended victim, to eventually land on innocent bystanders living in the lands below.]],name_ja=[[石の夜風]],},[973]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[974]={name_fr=[[La Nuit Du Chasseur]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Torama Queen]],name=[[Late Night Torama Queen]],class_level=60,help_en=[[When the sun falls on the Diadem, the islands' royalty comes out to revel 'neath the swollen moon. Said reveling may include the ransacking of expedition base camps, the destruction of airship rigging, and the devouring of leaden-legged adventurers.]],name_ja=[[狩人の夜]],},[975]={name_fr=[[La Nuit Du Chasseur]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Torama Queen]],name=[[Late Night Torama Queen]],class_level=60,help_en=[[When the sun falls on the Diadem, the islands' royalty comes out to revel 'neath the swollen moon. Said reveling may include the ransacking of expedition base camps, the destruction of airship rigging, and the devouring of leaden-legged adventurers.]],name_ja=[[狩人の夜]],},[976]={name_fr=[[Dévouement Aveugle]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Riskante Unternehmungen]],name=[[Mad Ventures In Retainer-sitting]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Not content with the paltry pickings his retainer was retrieving from ventures into the Black Shroud, a well-to-do noble recently ordered his humble hireling to the Diadem, forbidding the retainer's return until “treasure worthy of a king” was discovered. All the poor soul discovered, however, was a den of starving sky creatures, and now requires aid in escape.]],name_ja=[[無謀すぎた探索]],},[977]={name_fr=[[Amitié Entomologique]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Insektenbund]],name=[[Crawllateral Damage]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Scholars have determined that cloud crawlers are able to grow to sizes far exceeding that of their terra firma cousins in part due to killer ants which, in their pursuit of the sweet nectar excreted from the crawlers' pores, end up serving as a defense against predators.]],name_ja=[[雲海最大のヒモ]],},[978]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[979]={name_fr=[[Dévouement Aveugle]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Riskante Unternehmungen]],name=[[Mad Ventures In Retainer-sitting]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Not content with the paltry pickings his retainer was retrieving from ventures into the Black Shroud, a well-to-do noble recently ordered his humble hireling to the Diadem, forbidding the retainer's return until “treasure worthy of a king” was discovered. All the poor soul discovered, however, was a den of starving sky creatures, and now requires aid in escape.]],name_ja=[[無謀すぎた探索]],},[980]={name_fr=[[Les Dévoreuses De Couleurs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Regenbogenfresser]],name=[[I Can Wring A Rainbow]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Countless sky pirates claim that during their travels through the Sea of Clouds, they have, at one time or another, witnessed a massive bird attempting to devour a rainbow from the very heavens. Countless sky pirates also claim that they've slain sanuwas with their bare hands, bedded a thousand trollops, and downed entire barrels of rum in a single sitting.]],name_ja=[[虹を喰う者たち]],},[981]={name_fr=[[Les Dévoreuses De Couleurs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Regenbogenfresser]],name=[[I Can Wring A Rainbow]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Countless sky pirates claim that during their travels through the Sea of Clouds, they have, at one time or another, witnessed a massive bird attempting to devour a rainbow from the very heavens. Countless sky pirates also claim that they've slain sanuwas with their bare hands, bedded a thousand trollops, and downed entire barrels of rum in a single sitting.]],name_ja=[[虹を喰う者たち]],},[982]={name_fr=[[Les Dévoreuses De Couleurs]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Regenbogenfresser]],name=[[I Can Wring A Rainbow]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Countless sky pirates claim that during their travels through the Sea of Clouds, they have, at one time or another, witnessed a massive bird attempting to devour a rainbow from the very heavens. Countless sky pirates also claim that they've slain sanuwas with their bare hands, bedded a thousand trollops, and downed entire barrels of rum in a single sitting.]],name_ja=[[虹を喰う者たち]],},[983]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[984]={name_fr=[[Radiations Néfastes]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Elementarer Wahnsinn]],name=[[Excitable Boys]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Aether emitted by unstable elemental crystals is sending even the most docile of creatures into uncontrollable fits of madness. The condition appears to be irreversible, with a swift end the only means of granting these poor souls mercy.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの悪影響]],},[985]={name_fr=[[Les éléments S'éclatent!]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Scherbenhaufen]],name=[[Shard To Get]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Throughout the Diadem can be found crystals which have been rendered unstable by the extreme aetherial conditions experienced in the area. If the volatile energies within these fragments could somehow be harnessed, it could prove an invaluable boon to House Haillenarte.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの回収]],},[986]={name_fr=[[Les éléments S'éclatent!]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Scherbenhaufen]],name=[[Shard To Get]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Throughout the Diadem can be found crystals which have been rendered unstable by the extreme aetherial conditions experienced in the area. If the volatile energies within these fragments could somehow be harnessed, it could prove an invaluable boon to House Haillenarte.]],name_ja=[[放属性シャードの回収]],},[987]={name_fr=[[Les éléments S'éclatent!]],class_level_max=60,patch={number=[[3.55b]],},name_de=[[Scherbenhaufen]],name=[[Shard To Get]],class_level=60,help_en=[[Throughout the Diadem can be found crystals which have been rendered unstable by the extreme aetherial conditions experienced in the area. If the volatile energies within these fragments could somehow be harnessed, it could prove an invaluable boon to House Haillenarte.]],name_ja=[[放属